(2158, 'Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainer', 'Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainers in Light Ultra Marine, Pure Platinum. The Air VaporMax 2023 lights the way towards that ‘walking on Air’ sensation that only Nike can provide. Awash with innovative tech via the removable perforated sock liner and stretchy Flyknit upper that’s made from at least 20% recycled content by weight. The one-piece Air unit that patrols the entire length of the shoe allows for smoother transitions and throws in unreal levels of cushioning. Standard lacing, seamless collar that sculpts the ankle reducing hot spots, and grippy rubber outsole. After the 7-year journey from conception to release, the Air VaporMax represents a new era in Nike innovation. To truly capture the feeling of \"running on air\", the designers restructured the Air unit to be attached directly to the upper. As you step down, each lug gets pushed into the Air unit, ramping up the pressure. Then, as you step off, the pressure releases creating springy bounce with superior flexibility.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095128.jpg'),
(2159, 'Air Max 95 Essential Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 95 Essential Trainers in Wolf Grey, Rugged Orange and Black. Inspired by the human body, the inimitable Air Max 95 Essential sees the midsole representing the spine, graduated panels are the muscles, the lace loops are the shoe’s ribs and the mesh draping the upper is the skin. The breathable mesh upper features leather and synthetic leather reinforcements, whilst the innovative lacing system supplies a snug custom fit. Visible Air cushioning, and flex grooves in the grippy outsole bend with your foot for unrestrictive movement. Signature Nike branding throughout.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095132.jpg'),
(2161, 'Nike Blazer Low \'77 Jumbo', 'They say, \"Don\'t fix what works\". We say, \"Perfect it\". The classic, streetwear superstar gets rethought with the Nike Blazer Low \'77 Jumbo. Harnessing the old-school look you love, it now features an oversized Swoosh design and jumbo laces. Its plush foam tongue and thicker stitching embolden the iconic look that\'s been praised by the streets since \'77.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/8bd81405-bbe2-4516-aecb-665e22981785/blazer-low-77-jumbo-shoes-FTNGmV.png'),
(2162, 'Air Max Pulse Roam Trainer', 'Nike Air Max Pulse Roam Trainers in Dark Smoke Grey and Iron Grey. Unveiled for Air Max day 2023 the debut of the Air Max Pulse roam takes the Pulse aesthetic heritage look and gives it a whole new vibe. A new trainer from Nike that combines the comfort and style of the Air Max Pulse with the ruggedness of a trail shoe. It features a durable upper made of synthetic leather and mesh, as well as a cushioned midsole with Air Max cushioning for a comfortable ride. The outsole is made of rubber for traction on a variety of surfaces.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095136.jpg'),
(2163, 'Air Max Pulse Roam Trainer', 'Nike Air Max Pulse Roam Trainers in Stone, Light Bone, Summit White. Unveiled for Air Max day 2023 the debut of the Air Max Pulse roam takes the Pulse aesthetic heritage look and gives it a whole new vibe. A new trainer from Nike that combines the comfort and style of the Air Max Pulse with the ruggedness of a trail shoe. It features a durable upper made of synthetic leather and mesh, as well as a cushioned midsole with Air Max cushioning for a comfortable ride. The outsole is made of rubber for traction on a variety of surfaces.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095137.jpg'),
(2164, 'Air Force 1 Low Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 Low Trainers in White, Safety Orange and University Gold. Introduce your feet to some legendary footwear here in the form of the irresistible Air Force 1 from Nike. Effortlessly fusing cushioned court comfort with off-duty panache, the AF-1’s luscious leather upper adds a crisp and slick aesthetic whilst the underfoot is taken care of by the Nike Air unit that delivers comfort you can rely on again and again. Low-cut padded ankle collar, foam midsole, perforated toe box and pivot circle grippy rubber outsole. Spray-painted double Swoosh logos seal the deal.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088661.jpg'),
(2165, 'Air More \'96 \'Photon Dust\' Trainer', 'Nike Air More \'96 \'Photon Dust\' Trainers in Photon Dust, Metallic Silver, White and Black. Rocking 1990’s graffiti-styled graphics and sat atop visible Air cushioning, the Air More Uptempo ’96 absolutely nails down a jaw dropping off-court aesthetic. Originally designed for performance hoops, the Max Air unit is both lightweight and durable. The elastic straps that run across the top of the foot allow you to wear them laced or unlaced, whilst the round laces match the round pull tabs for another great style point. Interior graphics, heel pull tab, and large oversized Air logo to side. Not intended for use as Personal Protective Equipment (PPE).', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088680.jpg'),
(2167, 'Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainer', 'Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainers in Black and White. The Air VaporMax 2023 lights the way towards that ‘walking on Air’ sensation that only Nike can provide. Awash with innovative tech via the removable perforated sock liner and stretchy Flyknit upper that’s made from at least 20% recycled content by weight. The one-piece Air unit that patrols the entire length of the shoe allows for smoother transitions and throws in unreal levels of cushioning. Standard lacing, seamless collar that sculpts the ankle reducing hot spots, and grippy rubber outsole. After the 7-year journey from conception to release, the Air VaporMax represents a new era in Nike innovation. To truly capture the feeling of \"running on air\", the designers restructured the Air unit to be attached directly to the upper. As you step down, each lug gets pushed into the Air unit, ramping up the pressure. Then, as you step off, the pressure releases creating springy bounce with superior flexibility.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088681.jpg'),
(2168, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'Comfortable, durable and timeless—it\'s number 1 for a reason. The classic \'80s construction pairs with crisp real and synthetic leather and Nike Air cushioning for style that tracks whether you\'re on the court or on the go.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/77282e80-2e20-457b-a370-00debb7c9d74/air-force-1-07-shoes-pfJxVN.png'),
(2169, 'Air Force 1 \'07 Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 Trainers in White and Picante Red. The seamless combination of on-court comfort and off-court panache is astounding as you introduce your feet to some legendary footwear here in the form of the irresistible Air Force 1 from Nike. Effortlessly fusing cushioned court comfort with off-duty panache, the AF-1’s luscious leather upper adds a crisp and slick aesthetic whilst the underfoot is taken care of by the Nike Air unit that delivers comfort you can rely on again and again. Low-cut padded ankle collar, foam midsole, perforated toe box and pivot circle grippy rubber outsole. Outlined Swoosh to sides and customary contrast AIR motif.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091558.jpg'),
(2171, 'Air Max 90 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 90 Trainers in Smoke Grey, Black, Ash Silver and Light Silver. Originally designed for performance running, feel the purrrr of technical brilliance slot seamlessly into your everyday casual wear. Epitomising the 1990s world of art, music and culture, the striking aesthetics combine with a grippy Waffle outsole and visible lightweight Air cushioning to leave you walking on a cloud. Air technology first debuted in 1978, with its visible cousin later appearing in 1987 in the legendary Air Max 1’s.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091559.jpg'),
(2172, 'Air Huarache Runner Trainer', 'Nike Air Huarache Runner Trainers in Black, White, Sesame and Bright Crimson. A rework on the classic Huarache silhouette, the plush running-inspired cushioned outsole remains but now sat atop a more stable and constructed upper. Lashings of leather and suede panels throughout, understated swoosh branding and a rubber waffle outsole tread for added grip.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091571.jpg'),
(2173, 'Air Max TW Trainer', 'Nike Air Max TW Trainers in Black and Anthracite. That quintessential laid-back look of ‘90s footwear collides with fast-paced 100 miles per hour modern culture in the form of the inimitable Air Max Tailwind. Taking its cues from the beloved franchise that introduced us to Nike Air Max cushioning and smoothed that tricky transition from sportswear to streetwear, this striking design ticks all the style and comfort boxes. The lightweight breathable engineered upper showcases angular and organic lines, whilst the 5 see-through windows underfoot deliver time-tested Air cushioning. Grippy rubber outsole for enhanced traction.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091580.jpg'),
(2174, 'Air Force 1 \'07 Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 Trainers in White and Bronzine. The seamless combination of on-court comfort and off-court panache is astounding as you introduce your feet to some legendary footwear here in the form of the irresistible Air Force 1 from Nike. Effortlessly fusing cushioned court comfort with off-duty panache, the AF-1’s luscious leather upper adds a crisp and slick aesthetic whilst the underfoot is taken care of by the Nike Air unit that delivers comfort you can rely on again and again. Low-cut padded ankle collar, foam midsole, perforated toe box and pivot circle grippy rubber outsole. Outlined Swoosh to sides and customary contrast AIR motif.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4100572.jpg'),
(2175, 'Air Force 1 \'07', 'You can\'t stop ageing, but the Air Force 1 \'Fresh\' gets pretty close. Soft, textured leather helps conceal creasing, plus it\'s easy to clean. We\'ve swapped woven labels for debossed branding, while the perforated sockliner keeps it airy and breathable. An extra set of laces means you can go from grabbing coffee on the go to playing in the park without thinking twice. Now, there\'s really no reason not to rock your triple blacks morning \'til night—365.\nSKU: DM0211-001', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_prod_ss/w_640,c_limit,f_auto/f2b7f11f-628f-4fb7-afa1-66f7a51f52f0/air-force-1-07-fresh-dm0211-001-release-date.jpg'),
(2176, 'Air Force 1 \'07 3 Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 3 Trainers in Black and White. This low-cut take on the iconic Air Force 1 silhouette skilfully fuses a classic court aesthetic with a bold fashion-friendly look. Nike Air cushioning, perforated toe box and non-marking outsole.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4030375.jpg'),
(2178, 'Air VaporMax Plus Trainer', 'Nike Air VaporMax Plus Trainers in Black and Volt. 20+ years since the Air Max Plus debut; Nike combine the striking silhouette with a translucent VaporMax sole unit, tuned Air branding and 3M reflective detail.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4037932.jpg'),
(2180, 'Air VaporMax Plus Trainer', 'Nike Air VaporMax Plus Trainers in Black. 20 years since the Air Max Plus debut; Nike combine the striking silhouette with a translucent VaporMax sole unit, tuned Air branding and 3M reflective detail.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4050144.jpg'),
(2181, 'Air Max 95 WT Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 95 WT Trainers in Iron Grey, White and Volt. This premium fusion of unparalleled comfort and jaw-dropping style floats its way into your life via Footasylum. Taking its inspiration from the human body; the midsole represents the spine, graduated panels are the muscles. the laces are the ribs and the iconic side panels represent strength. Innovative lacing for ease of putting on and taking off, Nike Air technology that cushions and absorbs impact, breathable mesh upper reinforced with leather and synthetic overlays and a flex-grooved foam midsole.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4081559.jpg'),
(2182, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Never mistaken, the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 is the hardwood classic that redefined basketball shoes and sneaker culture forever. Suede details atop synthetic leather on the upper deliver the iconic style that landed it at the pinnacle of street, sport and culture for decades.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/i1-bf108f08-590a-4de7-94d2-f70b22b7f6b6/air-force-1-lv8-shoe-PB76g2.png'),
(2183, 'Air Force 1 Low Winterised Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 Low Winterised Trainers in White, Black and Volt. A staple in the footwear rotation since it\'s introduction in 1982, a chunky court-built Air Force has taken on many different iterations over the years. Seen here stripped back in a clean premium white leather, green volt swoosh taping to heel provides added contrast. Large contrast Swoosh to sides and a cushioned AIR sole complete.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4081568.jpg'),
(2184, 'Air Max 95 Essential Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 95 Essential Trainers in Black, Summit White and Gold Sesame. Inspired by the human body, the inimitable Air Max 95 Essential sees the midsole representing the spine, graduated panels are the muscles, the lace loops are the shoe’s ribs and the mesh draping the upper is the skin. The breathable mesh upper features leather and synthetic leather reinforcements, whilst the innovative lacing system supplies a snug custom fit. Visible Air cushioning, and flex grooves in the grippy outsole bend with your foot for unrestrictive movement. Signature Nike branding throughout.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4084275.jpg'),
(2186, 'Dunk Low Trainer', 'Nike Dunk Low Trainers in White, Blue and Grey. An easy way to make a statement with your outfit, this white and blue men\'s Dunk with a contrasting Swoosh to the side is easy to style day to night, making it a must-have in your sneaker rotation. The crisp white leather is layered with light blue panels and finished with the iconic Swoosh.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4084563.jpg'),
(2187, 'Air Max 270 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 270 Trainers in Wolf Grey, Black Iron and Blue Lightening. Legendary Air gets itself some extra Airtime at Footasylum here as the formidable Air Max 270 combines bold style with plush cushioning and cutting-edge innovations. Lightweight airy upper, cushioned low cut collar, stretchy inner sleeve and a bootie construction that gets up closed and personal. Foam midsole that puts a real spring in your step, Max Air unit to heel for long-lasting comfort and an extra-large window that delivers a bold style, pull tab to heel and grippy rubber outsole to complete.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4084565.jpg'),
(2188, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'The radiance lives on with the b-ball original. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, it puts a fresh spin on what you know best: \'80s-inspired construction, bold details and nothin\'-but-net style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/3f3e7049-5c99-428c-abcd-e246b086f2ed/air-force-1-07-shoes-VJhk3P.png'),
(2189, 'Air Force 1 \'07 Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 Trainers in Black and White. Introduce your feet to some legendary footwear here in the form of the irresistible Air Force 1 from Nike. Effortlessly fusing cushioned court comfort with off-duty panache, the AF-1’s luscious leather upper adds a crisp and slick aesthetic whilst the underfoot is taken care of by the Nike Air unit that delivers comfort you can rely on again and again. Low-cut padded ankle collar, foam midsole, perforated toe box and pivot circle grippy rubber outsole. Outlined Swoosh to sides and customary contrast AIR motif.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088659.jpg'),
