(2191, 'Dunk Low Retro Trainer', 'Nike Dunk Low Retro Trainers in White and Night Maroon. A simple yet effective style that features a clean white leather base with hits of Night Maroon on the Swoosh, tongue and heel. The shoe is made with a durable leather upper that is both comfortable and stylish. The Night Maroon accents add a touch of color and personality to the shoe, while the white midsole and outsole provide a clean and classic look.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088676.jpg'),
(2192, 'Air Max 90 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 90 Trainers in Neutral Olive and Sequoia. Originally designed for performance running, feel the purrrr of technical brilliance slot seamlessly into your everyday casual wear. Epitomising the 1990’s world of art, music and culture, the striking aesthetics combine with a grippy Waffle outsole and visible lightweight Air cushioning to leave you walking on a cloud. Air technology first debuted in 1978, with its visible cousin later appearing in 1987 in the legendary Air Max 1’s.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091578.jpg'),
(2193, 'Air Max 90 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 90 Trainers in Photon Dust and Light Thistle. Originally designed for performance running, feel the purrrr of technical brilliance slot seamlessly into your everyday casual wear. Epitomising the 1990’s world of art, music and culture, the striking aesthetics combine with a grippy Waffle outsole and visible lightweight Air cushioning to leave you walking on a cloud. Air technology first debuted in 1978, with its visible cousin later appearing in 1987 in the legendary Air Max 1’s.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091579.jpg'),
(2194, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven. The Air Max 90 stays true to its running roots with the iconic Waffle sole, stitched overlays and classic details. A bold, dark colourway contrasts with a gum outsole and reflective design details for a sleek look while Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/9e970183-c03c-4250-ae91-b238aefd47df/air-max-90-shoes-bVD4kw.png'),
(2195, 'Air Force 1 React Trainer', 'Nike Air Force 1 React Trainers in White, Sail and Black. Part of Nike’s Air Force 1 40th anniversary celebrations, plush React technology and amplified outsole gives this iconic silhouette a fresh injection of superiority. With polished gold accents, “82-22” sock liner prints and refreshed branding that fuses logos from past releases that pay tribute to this mighty institution. Secure lace fastening, padded collar and tongue, perforated tow box, and famous Nike branding.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091808.jpg'),
(2196, 'Air Max TW Trainer', 'Nike Air Max TW Trainers in Black, Blue Tint and Medium Ash. That quintessential laid-back look of ‘90s footwear collides with fast-paced 100 miles per hour modern culture in the form of the inimitable Air Max Tailwind. Taking its cues from the beloved franchise that introduced us to Nike Air Max cushioning and smoothed that tricky transition from sportswear to streetwear, this striking design ticks all the style and comfort boxes. The lightweight breathable engineered upper showcases angular and organic lines, whilst the 5 see-through windows underfoot deliver time-tested Air cushioning. Grippy rubber outsole for enhanced traction.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095139.jpg'),
(2197, 'Dunk Low Retro BTTYS Trainer', 'Nike Dunk Low Retro BTTYS Trainers in Polar and White. Designed to integrate that quintessential basketball influence onto a low-cut sneaker, this exquisite leather silhouette boasts premium panelled design and features a striking eye-catching colour scheme. Secure lace fastening, round perforated toe, signature Swoosh branding, branded tongue, branded heel counter and flat grippy rubber sole.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095140.jpg'),
(2198, 'Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainer', 'Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit Trainers in Pure Platinum, White and Anthracite. The Air VaporMax 2023 lights the way towards that ‘walking on Air’ sensation that only Nike can provide. Awash with innovative tech via the removable perforated sock liner and stretchy Flyknit upper that’s made from at least 20% recycled content by weight. The one-piece Air unit that patrols the entire length of the shoe allows for smoother transitions and throws in unreal levels of cushioning. Standard lacing, seamless collar that sculpts the ankle reducing hot spots, and grippy rubber outsole. After the 7-year journey from conception to release, the Air VaporMax represents a new era in Nike innovation. To truly capture the feeling of \"running on air\", the designers restructured the Air unit to be attached directly to the upper. As you step down, each lug gets pushed into the Air unit, ramping up the pressure. Then, as you step off, the pressure releases creating springy bounce with superior flexibility.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4091566.jpg'),
(2199, 'Nike Blazer Mid Pro Club', 'Being rooted doesn\'t mean you can\'t step forwards. Keeping the classic simplicity and comfort you love, your favourite wardrobe staple gets remastered for the modern era. Extra rubber extends from the midsole to the Swoosh for a bold twist (and a little nod to Nike innovation from the \'70s). The patchwork upper adds the perfect amount of retro attitude.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/dec25f7f-1f38-44af-83e7-c8f83974ac16/blazer-mid-pro-club-shoes-3wCtV7.png'),
(2200, 'Air Max 90 GTX Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 90 GTX Trainers in Black, Honeydew and Mica Green. A weatherized version of the classic Nike Air Max 90, a waterproof GORE-TEX upper to keep your feet dry in wet conditions, as well as a durable leather vamp for added protection. The shoe also retains the iconic Air Max bubble unit in the heel for responsive cushioning.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095119.jpg'),
(2201, 'Air Max 90 Terrascape Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Trainers in Sail and Black Sea Glass. Next up for Nike’s “Next Nature” series is this sustainable re-working of the iconic Air Max 90. Almost indistinguishable from its traditional counterpart, the lushly layered upper consists of a robust ripstop base and durable overlays, all sat upon visible Nike Air technology. The semi-translucent midsole and crater speckled outsole provide aesthetically pleasing backup. Signature Nike branding together with handy heel and tongue pull loops. This magnificent silhouette boasts around 20% recycled materials by weight, so your footprint on the earth is less impact but in no way less stylish.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4062747.jpg'),
(2202, 'Air Max 95 Essential Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 95 Essential Trainers in Anthracite, Black, Team Red and Summit White. Inspired by the human body, the inimitable Air Max 95 Essential sees the midsole representing the spine, graduated panels are the muscles, the lace loops are the shoe’s ribs and the mesh draping the upper is the skin. The breathable mesh upper features leather and synthetic leather reinforcements, whilst the innovative lacing system supplies a snug custom fit. Visible Air cushioning, and flex grooves in the grippy outsole bend with your foot for unrestrictive movement. Signature Nike branding throughout.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4081563.jpg'),
(2203, 'Huarache Trainer', 'Nike Huarache Trainers in White and Pure Platinum. First released in 1991, esteemed footwear designer Tinker Hatfield wished to combine the fit of neoprene water-ski boots with the sheer functionality of South American sandals. Thirty years later, this instant classic is still a favourite on the basketball courts and on the streets where it really earned respect. With a plush foam midsole that is soft and springy, the distinctive heel clip and minimal branding channel a real early 1990’s vibe. Soft leather and airy neoprene-like fabric combine for laid-back styling. Cushioned inner sleeve, durable grippy rubber outsole and variable-width lacing enhance your comfort whilst perforations allow for increased breathability. Huarache motif to tongue.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4063274.jpg'),
(2204, 'Air Max 270 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 270 Trainers in Black and Light Bone. Footasylum gets up close and personal with the superlative Air Max 270 silhouette as its staggering 270-degree underfoot cushioning leaves us walking on Air. Futuristic styling and breathable upper.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/118712.jpg'),
(2205, 'Air Max Plus x F.C. Barcelona x Patta', 'Step into the pulse of Culers del Món. Designed in collaboration with Patta—the iconic Amsterdam label—this Air Max Plus continues a long tradition of partnership between F.C. Barcelona and Dutch visionaries. A fluid gradient of Deep Royal Blue and Noble Red paints the upper and midfoot plate, proving your blood runs blaugrana. Barça club crests grace the special-edition dubraes, while the lace tips evoke the stripes of the Senyera. To wrap it up, polished design lines add the unmistakable Air Max Plus aesthetic—another bold reminder of the heritage of greatness.\nSKU: FN8260-001', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_prod_ss/w_640,c_limit,f_auto/9057182b-dad8-4c30-8e68-40a62adfc006/air-max-plus-x-f-c-barcelona-x-patta-culers-del-m%C3%B3n-fn8260-001-release-date.jpg'),
(2206, 'Full Force Low Trainer', 'Nike Full Force Low Trainers in White, Polar, Black and Team Orange. A newer silhouette that takes all the loved features of classic court shoes. a low-cut design for a comfortable fit with a chunky sole unit really take ques from 80\'s basketball footwear. Built with a soft leather upper that is designed to age even softer, high sidewalls to the heel and toe aid durability and signature Nike swoosh sits to sides. A real interesting adaptation of the legendary AF1 DNA perfect for your daily rotation.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095144.jpg'),
(2207, 'Dunk Low Trainer', 'Nike Dunk Low Trainer in White and Picante Red, Introducing your new favourite Dunk. Designed for the every day, the Nike Dunk Low is a colourway that will go with every look. Keeping it simple, a white base allows a bold red Swoosh and outsole to take centre stage. A perforated toe box adds breathability and a full-length cushioned midsole delivers next-level comfort. Designed by Peter Moore in 1985, the Nike Dunk quickly became an icon on and off the courts. From its beginnings as a college basketball trainer to collaborations with Stüssy, Virgil Abloh, Supreme and Travis Scott, the Nike Dunk has cemented itself as one of the most iconic trainers of all time.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4099639.jpg'),
(2208, 'Full Force Low Trainer', 'Nike Full Force Low Trainers in White, Black Pewter, Sail and Team Orange. A newer silhouette that takes all the loved features of classic court shoes. a low-cut design for a comfortable fit with a chunky sole unit really take ques from 80\'s basketball footwear. Built with a soft leather upper that is designed to age even softer, high sidewalls to the heel and toe aid durability and signature Nike swoosh sits to sides. A real interesting adaptation of the legendary AF1 DNA perfect for your daily rotation.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4095143.jpg'),
(2209, 'Air Max 97 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 97 Trainers in White and Wolf Grey. Speeding into Footasylum with sleek, clean lines; the standout Air Max 97 returns with an innovative lacing system, lightweight performance and responsive, long lasting cushioning.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/122929.jpg'),
(2210, 'Air Jordan 1 Low SE', 'Fresh look, familiar feel. Every time the AJ1 gets a remake, you get the classic sneaker in new colours and textures. Premium materials and accents give modern expression to an all-time favourite.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/b5013570-56f0-4f6b-8199-ed697008bd9a/air-jordan-1-low-se-shoes-Z8CHrq.png'),
