(2215, 'Waffle One Trainer', 'Nike Waffle One Trainers in Summit White. A fitting tribute to the original shoe that catapulted Nike to success. Founder Bill Bowerman utilised a waffle iron to create a sole that delivered unparalleled traction. Soft foam cushioning.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4056085.jpg'),
(2216, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'Lace up and feel the legacy. Produced at the intersection of art, music and culture, this champion running shoe helped define the \'90s. Worn by presidents, revolutionised through collabs and celebrated with rare colourways, its striking visuals, Waffle outsole and exposed Air cushioning keep it alive and well.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/d5e6380d-af13-4c8a-829f-7177b94d100a/air-max-90-shoes-QBB9hs.png'),
