(2218, 'React Vision Trainer', 'Nike React Vision Trainers in White, University Blue and Deep Royal Blue. Comfort of this magnitude doesn’t come around often; the React Vision skilfully combines lushly layered textures, vivid colours and a revolutionary seamless mesh upper complete with subtle pattern. Nike’s React foam offers up supreme all-day comfort whilst the deluxe tongue teams up with the padded heel for comfort you can trust. Eye-catching DIY-like exposed stitching, patchwork eye stays, Printed pull tabs, outlined Swoosh logo and rubber pods on the sole that boost the robustness and grip.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088678.jpg'),
(2219, 'Air Max TW Trainer', 'Nike Air Max TW Trainers in White, Spruce and Black. That quintessential laid-back look of ‘90s footwear collides with fast-paced 100 miles per hour modern culture in the form of the inimitable Air Max Tailwind. Taking its cues from the beloved franchise that introduced us to Nike Air Max cushioning and smoothed that tricky transition from sportswear to streetwear, this striking design ticks all the style and comfort boxes. The lightweight breathable engineered upper showcases angular and organic lines, whilst the 5 see-through windows underfoot deliver time-tested Air cushioning. Grippy rubber outsole for enhanced traction.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088686.jpg'),
(2220, 'Air Max 97 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 97 Trainers in Black and White. Speeding into Footasylum with sleek, clean lines; the standout Air Max 97 returns with an innovative lacing system, lightweight performance and responsive, long lasting cushioning.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/122927.jpg'),
(2221, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Meet the leader of the pack. Walking on clouds above the noise, the Air Max 1 blends timeless design with cushioned comfort. Sporting a fast-paced look, wavy mudguard and Nike Air, this classic icon hit the scene in \'87 and continues to be the soul of the franchise today.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/ffc3809a-2851-4d96-b8f3-ecde6ac63eef/air-max-1-shoes-FqGhHQ.png'),
(2222, 'React Vision Trainer', 'Nike React Vision Trainers in Black and White. Comfort of this magnitude doesn’t come around often; the React Vision skilfully combines lushly layered textures, vivid colours and a revolutionary seamless mesh upper complete with subtle pattern. Nike’s React foam offers up supreme all-day comfort whilst the deluxe tongue teams up with the padded heel for comfort you can trust. Eye-catching DIY-like exposed stitching, patchwork eye stays, D/MS/X label on pull tabs and insole, outlined Swoosh logo and rubber pods on the sole that boost the robustness and grip.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4037634.jpg'),
(2223, 'Air Max 270 Trainer', 'Nike Air Max 270 Trainers in White, Black and Volt. Legendary Air gets itself some extra Airtime at Footasylum here as the formidable Air Max 270 combines bold style with plush cushioning and cutting-edge innovations. Lightweight airy upper, cushioned low cut collar, stretchy inner sleeve and a bootie construction that gets up closed and personal. Foam midsole that puts a real spring in your step, Max Air unit to heel for long-lasting comfort and an extra-large window that delivers a bold style, pull tab to heel and grippy rubber outsole to complete.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4043605.jpg'),
(2224, 'Blazer Mid \'77 Jumbo Trainer', 'Nike Blazer Mid \'77 Jumbo Trainers in White and Black. This endearing silhouette gets itself a much-deserved facelift whilst still maintaining the features that made it a hit in the first place. Still channelling that vintage aesthetic, it now boasts an elastic heel complete with corduroy-style texture and large exaggerated pull tabs for your convenience. The spirit of the classic Blazer lives on through the stitched leather overlays and soft suede accents, whilst the oversized Nike Swoosh design and jumbo laces will add a fun twist to any look. Thick exposed foam tongue, thick stitching and raised herringbone pattern to the rubber outsole.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4062743.jpg'),
(2225, 'Flight \'89 Trainer', 'Nike Flight \'89 Trainers in White, Black and Light Smoke Grey. Starting off life as a basketball performance silhouette back in 1989, fast forward to 2022 and that distinctive vintage aesthetic is still evident. With a lush leather upper, bold contrast trims, secure lace fastening, and large Air Flight branding to tongue. Visible Air sole unit, embroidered heel branding and famous Nike Swoosh to sides.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4081577.jpg'),
(2226, 'Air Flight Lite Mid Leather Trainer', 'Nike Air Flight Lite Mid Leather Trainers in White and Black. Embellished with a luxurious velvety leather upper for premium high-end stylish comfort. Lightweight airy wear is attained thanks to the perforations that keep the air flow moving whilst the padded ankle collar adds enhanced support. The robust plastic accents to the eyelets add a distinct retro basketball aesthetic. Lining has graphic print throughout that runs down the collar, soft foam in midsole and durable grippy rubber outsole.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4081582.jpg'),
(2227, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Never mistaken, the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 is the hardwood classic that redefined basketball shoes and sneaker culture forever. Suede details atop synthetic leather on the upper deliver the iconic style that landed it at the pinnacle of street, sport and culture for decades.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/5dd4d11f-44bb-4df5-aca5-5c44f1aec127/air-force-1-lv8-shoe-nWX5tl.png'),
(2228, 'Air Max TW Trainer', 'Nike Air Max TW Trainers in Flat Pewter and Obsidian White. That quintessential laid-back look of ‘90s footwear collides with fast-paced 100 miles per hour modern culture in the form of the inimitable Air Max Tailwind. Taking its cues from the beloved franchise that introduced us to Nike Air Max cushioning and smoothed that tricky transition from sportswear to streetwear, this striking design ticks all the style and comfort boxes. The lightweight breathable engineered upper showcases angular and organic lines, whilst the 5 see-through windows underfoot deliver time-tested Air cushioning. Grippy rubber outsole for enhanced traction.', 'https://www.footasylum.com/images/products/large/4088662.jpg'),
(2229, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'Comfortable, durable and timeless—it\'s number 1 for a reason. Classic \'80s construction pairs with durable leather and Ripstop textiles for a sturdy construction. Nike Air cushioning delivers lasting comfort while reflective design details and a frosted blue outsole add bold style that tracks whether you\'re on the court or on the go.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/ef549c11-cf24-468e-829f-7c4feb56f9b8/air-force-1-07-shoes-z3Pm1M.png'),
(2230, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'The \'80s basketball icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. Channelling vintage style back onto the streets, its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/dcc1a3ac-ff45-4a70-939e-53d1eb7244b0/dunk-low-shoes-7TNTvF.png'),
(2231, 'Nike Air Max Plus III', 'The Nike Air Max Plus III combines ultra-comfortable Tuned Air Technology with an energetic silhouette made famous by its predecessors. The III updates the look with TPU details fused to the upper while paying homage to the iconic colour fade.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/aqcdmfttkq4cuvv9nuwx/air-max-plus-iii-shoes-trH9dX.png'),
(2232, 'Air Jordan 5 \'Navy\'', 'Step into a classic with the AJ5 \'Navy\'. A mix of premium suede and durable canvas creates a distinct material expression, while the Midnight Navy and Football Grey combine for a bold finish. Lace locks keep your look anchored to the spirit of \'90s hoops. The signature Tinker Hatfield design maintains the stylised midsole, vented panels and Jumpman-branded tongue that make it an icon—but the icy, translucent outsole and smoky plastic accents keep it feeling brand new.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/36d03e6f-614e-47b3-a950-1fb12fbc023f/air-jordan-5-navy-shoes-rbPg6p.png'),
(2233, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'Ground your look in legendary style with this hoops original. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, the Nike Air Force 1 \'07 puts a fresh spin on everything you love most about the AF-1. Its durable leather on the upper looks sleek and crisp while Nike Air units underfoot add comfortable cushioning. Spray-paint-inspired double Swoosh logos finish off the design with just the right amount of nothing-but-net style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/e6a85daa-1a77-45b9-a892-b4e72124060f/air-force-1-07-shoes-WcsvD0.png'),
(2234, 'Nike P-6000', 'A mash-up of Pegasus\' past, the Nike P-6000 features breathable mesh with horizontal and vertical overlays for a 2000s running look that is as striking as, say, a majestic winged horse. Drawing on the design of the Nike Pegasus 25 and 2006, its running aesthetic meets all-day comfort for the streets.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/6b257d85-cbc4-4179-badd-b6c81e290926/p-6000-shoes-2FBrXk.png'),
(2235, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'Nike\'s first lifestyle Air Max brings you style, comfort and big attitude in the Nike Air Max 270. The design draws inspiration from Air Max icons, showcasing Nike\'s greatest innovation with its large window and fresh array of colours.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/skwgyqrbfzhu6uyeh0gg/air-max-270-shoes-mVp8wh.png'),
(2236, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'Score major points in this legendary classic. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, this hoops original pairs crisp neutral leather with pops of electric colour for nothing-but-net style. Hidden Nike Air unit and durable, era-echoing \'80s construction add the comfort you know and love.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/c46f5069-1d99-4775-ace0-e01c2f587041/air-force-1-07-shoes-PMVSKW.png'),
(2237, 'Nike Air Max Plus Utility', 'Inspired by the beach but made for city streets, the Nike Air Max Plus Utility gets a rugged upgrade perfect for your urban adventures. We added a sturdy suede mudguard to its breathable knit upper and tightened the look up with an extra set of toggle-closure laces for a secure and supportive fit. Plus, visible Max Air units in the forefoot and heel provide a Tuned Air experience that blends comfort with defiant style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/84fdcee0-c38c-443c-bfef-2c5148438bd9/air-max-plus-utility-shoes-kZZ2vm.png'),
(2238, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 WB', 'The legend lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 \'07 WB, a low-cut take on the iconic AF-1 that offers classic court style and premium cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/9586f004-25c7-4e72-bef9-6492f6491a4b/air-force-1-07-wb-shoe-vq8HPw.png'),
(2239, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, this \'80s b-ball icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. Supple, monochromatic leather overlays and pops of colour help this Dunk channel vintage style while its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/e424c86b-08a1-4d79-ac1b-660e7d34afc8/dunk-low-shoes-LBHrkd.png'),
(2240, 'Nike Air Max Plus', 'The Nike Air Max Plus Men\'s Shoe brings back the legendary \'Tuned\' Air cushioning and energetic design lines of the 1998 original.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/b97830fb-c11f-41d8-873e-bcb41aa58458/air-max-plus-shoe-wK86SQ.png'),
(2241, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Ground your look in throwback hoops flair with the Dunk Low. Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, this sneaker icon returns with a durable leather upper and knit accents inspired by vintage denim. Its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/47b5e2f1-aa3d-4ed2-bb5e-e902bb756841/dunk-low-shoes-5vNTF2.png'),
(2242, 'Nike Air Max 95 Essential', 'The Nike Air Max 95 Essential takes design cues from the human body. The midsole represents the spine, graduated panels are the muscles, the lace loops are the shoe\'s ribs and the mesh on the upper is the skin.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/e20484c2-2b66-4124-b692-ad132a4ef9a5/air-max-95-essential-shoe-KffNK0.png'),
(2243, 'Nike Air Max SYSTM', 'Looks Max, feels Max. The Air Max SYSTM brings back everything you love about your favourite \'80s vibes (without the parachute trousers). Tried-and-tested visible Nike Air cushioning pairs with a sleek, sport-inspired upper. It\'s Air Max delivering again.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/e448ee74-8d67-4332-b18c-4d1640f78dac/air-max-systm-shoes-HtKpnG.png'),
(2244, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the Dunk returns with classic details and throwback hoops style. Its padded, low-cut collar and vintage design lets you take your game anywhere—comfortably.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/40adbbb5-5f00-41d5-9eed-1e0e744c236d/dunk-low-shoes-C5dwf3.png'),
(2245, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'Lace up and feel the legacy. Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven. The Air Max 90 stays true to its running roots with the iconic Waffle sole, stitched overlays and classic details. Durable leather pairs with Ripstop textiles for a sturdy construction. Plus, visible Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/bfc04b0f-32d9-48a9-b4b7-7acb7fbcb54b/air-max-90-shoes-bnz7pN.png'),
(2246, 'Air Jordan 1 Mid SE', 'Fresh look, familiar feel. Every time the AJ1 gets a remake, you get the classic sneaker in new colours and textures. Premium materials and accents give modern expression to an all-time favourite.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/6dd5c76b-c124-45f3-952e-a89d0741bcdf/air-jordan-1-mid-se-shoes-bcVdbQ.png'),
(2247, 'NikeCourt Royale 2 Next Nature', 'A flash from the past meets modern times. The NikeCourt Royale 2 Next Nature is made from at least 20% recycled content by weight. We intentionally replaced high-impact leather with synthetic leather for a crisp look that\'s smooth and is easy to wear. The large, retro Swoosh adds throwback appeal.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/f6b0250d-541e-4535-acef-f98a6174cc18/nikecourt-royale-2-next-nature-shoes-Jwwfww.png'),
(2248, 'Nike Air Max TW', 'So you\'re in love with the classic look of the \'90s, but you\'ve got a thing for today\'s fast-paced culture. Meet the Air Max TW. Inspired by the treasured franchise that brought Nike Air cushioning to the world and laid the foundation for the track-to-street aesthetic, its eye-catching design delivers a 1–2 punch of comfort and fashion. Ready to highlight any \'fit, its lightweight upper pairs angular and organic lines to create an entrancing haptic effect. The contrasting colourways make it easy to style. And if you\'re ready for the next step, the 5 windows underfoot deliver a modern edge to visible Air cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/06b754f8-09d3-4a15-a459-e37e955d6d08/air-max-tw-shoes-2fb6jT.png'),
(2249, 'Jumpman Two Trey', 'Like \"Two Trey\" on MJ\'s licence plate, let your presence be known. This new generation of Jordan celebrates Mike\'s time in Chicago, complete with high-quality leather uppers and Air cushioned soles. Made as an homage to the on-court styles worn during his championship years, the Two Trey\'s midsole design references both the AJ11 and the AJ12.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/360cc5e1-a404-4a0d-b6a7-b7c415ed4282/jumpman-two-trey-shoes-bqMXW0.png'),
(2250, 'Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit', 'Have you ever walked on Air? Step into the Air VaporMax 2023 to see how it\'s done. The innovative tech is revealed through the perforated sockliner (pull it out to see more). The stretchy Flyknit upper is made from at least 20% recycled content by weight.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/c82627ea-5151-4ef1-904b-9c11f802ffc1/air-vapormax-2023-flyknit-shoes-v0z50N.png'),
(2251, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, this \'80s b-ball icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. The supple leather overlays help the Nike Dunk channel vintage style while its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/7740c7a6-d712-4a93-b58a-872f12b50cce/dunk-low-shoes-zPX1B1.png'),
(2252, 'Air Jordan 1 Mid SE', 'Get into some summery fun in your new fave AJ1s. Made with a combination of suede and canvas, this pair gives you the comfort you know and love with a seasonal update.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/22b7ce96-431b-432a-bd1a-ed32894a4430/air-jordan-1-mid-se-shoes-RN1mtn.png'),
(2253, 'Nike Air Max Flyknit Racer Next Nature', 'Paying homage to both heritage and innovation, we\'ve blended 2 icons (old and new) to go beyond what\'s expected in the Nike Air Max Flyknit Racer. Incredibly light and stretchy Flyknit is paired with oh-so-soft cushioning. Lace up and let your feet do the talking.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/2c351862-7f1e-4b5e-8a99-7a4092950505/air-max-flyknit-racer-next-nature-shoes-013sfX.png'),
(2254, 'Nike Air Max 95 Ultra', 'A running-inspired classic, the Nike Air Max 95 Ultra is a special lightweight edition that includes a sleek upper with the signature wavy design lines and airy mesh. The Max Air units give you supportive cushioning with every step, while reflective design details bring some shine to this iconic look.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/9c756a1e-81f8-41b1-8c82-778e79a5ad03/air-max-95-ultra-shoe-TQJj1w.png'),
(2255, 'Nike Dunk Low Retro', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the \'80s basketball icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. Its padded, low-cut collar and foam midsole let you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/4f8049c6-d329-4907-905b-df905c3da623/dunk-low-retro-shoes-66lZMB.png'),
(2256, 'Nike Dunk Low Retro', 'The \'80s b-ball icon returns with mixed materials and throwback hoops flair. Channel vintage style back onto the streets with aged and distressed details. Its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/721677ee-4921-4d48-950c-458e16b59e97/dunk-low-retro-shoes-H1MP1X.png'),
(2257, 'Nike Air VaporMax 2023 Flyknit', 'Have you ever walked on Air? Step into the Air VaporMax 2023 to see how it\'s done. The innovative tech is revealed through the perforated sockliner (pull it out to see more). The stretchy Flyknit upper is made from at least 20% recycled content by weight.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/f71c2a6d-9358-4949-86b9-1cdde924f9c6/air-vapormax-2023-flyknit-shoes-PRxpTh.png'),
(2258, 'NikeCourt Royale 2 Next Nature', 'A flash from the past meets modern times. The NikeCourt Royale 2 Next Nature is made from at least 20% recycled content by weight. We intentionally replaced high-impact leather with synthetic leather for a crisp look that\'s smooth and is easy to wear. The large, retro Swoosh adds throwback appeal.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/a73a7f08-07b0-4595-80a4-ed427dea1b79/nikecourt-royale-2-next-nature-shoes-mKwDkC.png'),
(2259, 'Nike Air Max Plus', 'Make some waves in the Nike Air Max Plus, a Tuned Air experience that offers premium stability and cushioning. A breathable knit upper works with wavy design lines, a gum outsole and polished plastic accents around the toe to blend comfort with defiant style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/c5acc3f1-b2c3-4279-ad0d-02e57209c784/air-max-plus-shoes-S7dFMv.png'),
(2260, 'Jumpman MVP', 'We didn\'t invent the remix—but considering the material we get to sample, this one\'s a no-brainer. We took elements from the AJ6, 7 and 8, making them into a completely new shoe that celebrates MJ\'s first 3-peat championship run. With leather, textile and nubuck details, these sneakers honour one legacy while encouraging you to cement your own.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/117890a6-97f0-457b-9550-80baf31ea1ea/jumpman-mvp-shoes-h3rXtZ.png'),
(2261, 'Nike Air Max 90 Premium', 'Lace up and feel the legacy in a champion running shoe that helped define the \'90s. Worn by presidents, revolutionised through collabs and celebrated through rare colourways, the Waffle outsole, its striking visuals and exposed Nike Air cushioning keep it alive and well.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/bdc0eef2-4176-4969-af7b-612793267ab7/air-max-90-shoes-fswxZN.png'),
(2262, 'Air Max Plus OG', 'Bring some heat to the street with this white-hot Air Max Plus design. Airbrush-inspired ghost flame graphics throughout the upper charge up your style, while Shiny Black and Metallic Silver accents add flash. And in classic Air Max Plus style, Tuned Air underfoot adds stability, responsive cushioning and an elevated feel.\nSKU: DZ3531-400', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_prod_ss/w_640,c_limit,f_auto/28457402-5ff2-482c-8b9f-627c98d93a07/air-max-plus-og-multi-colour-dz3531-400-release-date.jpg'),
(2263, 'Nike Air Max Plus 3', 'Featuring the same Tuned Air technology as its predecessors, the Nike Air Max Plus 3 updates the look with TPU fused to the upper while paying homage to the iconic colour fade of the OG.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/f21a648c-4017-442c-b1c6-270b28fab14d/air-max-plus-3-shoes-q8XPFv.png'),
(2264, 'Air Jordan 1 Low', 'Inspired by the original that debuted in 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Low offers a clean, classic look that\'s familiar yet always fresh. With an iconic design that pairs perfectly with any \'fit, these kicks ensure you\'ll always be on point.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/36d5c869-2322-4446-b1fb-3e783493d87e/air-jordan-1-low-shoes-QnthX1.png'),
(2265, 'Nike React Live', 'All day, every day, the Nike React Live lets you shine, mixing innovation like the cable lacing system with the smooth, comfortable ride of React technology. Its exposed needlework and mixed-material upper add DIY appeal while its low-cut athletics silhouette nods to the history of Nike running.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/34d5c4ac-ccc4-484f-b30b-6a4a374ea9a0/react-live-shoe-cdMN3k.png'),
(2266, 'Nike Air Max Plus', 'Let your attitude have the edge in the Air Max Plus, a tuned Air experience that offers premium cushioning and stability. Featuring airy mesh, polished accents and the original wavy design lines, it celebrates your defiant style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/495e33b9-cfd3-4f80-a275-030444c910e0/air-max-plus-shoes-49hns6.png'),
(2267, 'Nike React Vision', 'Add more responsiveness to your daily run. Revolutionary Nike Foam and a wide, rocker-shaped base bring energy return, impact attenuation and stability to every stride.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/6ba2001d-d4b7-41d3-a210-ed59644b2850/react-vision-running-shoes-01ZBnl.png'),
(2268, 'Jordan Post', 'Quick, comfy, cool. These slides are made from robust, flexible foam that will stay secure as you rack up those steps. Wide foot coverage holds your feet in place while the asymmetrical design gives you a distinct look.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/846b69f9-2bd3-4578-b156-dc1697abaff7/jordan-post-slides-X4rlC3.png'),
(2269, 'Nike Dunk High Retro', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the \'80s basketball icon returns with perfectly sheened overlays and original university colours. With its classic hoops design, the Nike Dunk High Retro channels \'80s vintage back onto the streets while its padded, high-top collar adds an old-school look rooted in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/5e7687f1-c13e-4bac-8ffa-a6f863ae9157/dunk-high-retro-shoe-lwQDx7.png'),
(2270, 'Nike React Vision', 'The Nike React Vision is a story of surreal comfort. Layered textures, playful shapes and a monochromatic colourway come together in a design influenced by the exaggerated world of our dreams. Nike React foam and an ultra-plush tongue help provide dreamlike cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/6e2eccc2-ca7e-4e0c-b84e-35465b4acf8f/react-vision-shoes-JNqsXt.png'),
(2271, 'Air Jordan 1 Low FlyEase', 'Lock in your style with this AJ1. We kept everything you love about the classic design—premium leather, Air cushioning, iconic Wings logo—while adding the Nike FlyEase closure system to make on and off a breeze. Getting out the door is now quicker than ever: just strap and zip.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/9259e44d-8e6a-4253-aefa-7db9720ea2b4/air-jordan-1-low-flyease-easy-on-off-shoes-XP8BFW.png'),
(2272, 'Nike Air Huarache', 'Built to fit your foot and designed for comfort, the Nike Air Huarache brings back a street-level favourite. Soft leather accents on the upper are mixed with super-breathable, perfectly shined neoprene-like fabric for easy styling. The low-cut collar and bootie-like construction keep it sleek. Its iconic heel clip and stripped away branding keep the early-90s look you love.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/be3d1f8d-9219-4fd6-b611-a1f7cde72800/air-huarache-shoes-66bm4c.png'),
(2273, 'Nike Air Max 97', 'Push your style into the future with the Nike Air Max 97. The rippled design lines give this iconic sneaker a sleek and fast-paced look, while a mix of materials adds a retro aesthetic with a premium feel. Of course, we kept the full-length Nike Air cushioning, letting you capture the spotlight in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/a25a1901-a687-4dd3-94f7-472e7af433aa/air-max-97-shoes-dVzGV3.png'),
(2274, 'Nike Air Max TW Next Nature', 'Meet the Nike Air Max TW, a treasured sneaker that updates a classic \'90s look for today\'s fast-paced world. Inspired by the franchise that brought Nike Air cushioning to the world, the eye-catching design merges comfort with cutting-edge style. Angular lines and a distinct mix of materials add depth and dimension while 5 windows in the midsole give you a modern look at Max Air cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/ce33183c-a4c3-4019-8573-0c769e460996/air-max-tw-next-nature-shoes-PscFgn.png'),
(2275, 'Nike Dunk Low Retro', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the basketball icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. Channelling \'80s vibes, its padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/917676dc-96b6-40f8-9a1f-da3917ca6967/dunk-low-retro-shoes-MMCRdG.png'),
(2276, 'Air Jordan 1 Mid', 'Inspired by the original AJ1, this mid-top edition maintains the iconic look you love while choice colours and crisp leather give it a distinct identity.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/179c8229-aab7-4e86-8d07-c65ab8dc3dad/air-jordan-1-mid-shoes-RkZ7vG.png'),
(2277, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'Legendary Air gets lifted. Our first lifestyle Air Max brings you comfort, bold style and 270 degrees of Air to showcase one of our greatest innovations yet. Add a lightweight, airy upper and a low-cut collar and you\'ve got the perfect kicks for everyday fun.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/5b698a8a-c3ad-4ddf-9b4c-844c18c0db73/air-max-270-shoes-0MJn2d.png'),
(2278, 'Nike Victori One', 'You\'ve played hard. You\'ve sweated. You\'ve given your all. Now there\'s just one last thing—you have to hit the showers. Don\'t worry, we\'ve got your back with the Nike Victori One. Its one-piece foam design feels soft and comfortable while traction patterns on the sole help with wet surfaces. They dry quickly too, so no one will know you\'ve just stepped out of the showers as you slide up to the party.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/c382b2ba-ca29-4527-a2d2-f4e90f87d7bc/victori-one-shower-slides-t6lCdT.png'),
(2279, 'Nike Defy All Day', 'Take on everyday challenges in the Nike Defy All Day. Leather up top and rubber traction on the bottom create a durable design that lasts the rigours of tough training sessions. Soft cushioning carries comfort through your workout—or a day of getting things done.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/eb0c5724-d3ab-42a6-891b-5be3afc92d83/defy-all-day-training-shoe-s1cPct.png'),
(2280, 'Nike Air Max Plus 3', 'Taking the best from past generations, this Air Max Plus 3 honours Air heritage with subtle nods to its predecessors. Soft foam and Max Air units put tried-and-tested bounce and comfort in your step. Futuristic design lines and gradient neutrals contrast with a Gum sole to bring these kicks into the present day with eye-catching style.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/5a72f3a7-cb6a-45d7-ab22-974ab411b11b/air-max-plus-3-shoes-6VV139.png'),
(2281, 'Jordan Point Lane', 'The Jordan Point Lane mixes elements from game shoes MJ wore during 3 of his most memorable seasons.Named after his Chicago address, this mash-up pulls in bits and pieces from the AJ3, AJ6 and AJ11 to create a shoe that\'s inspired by greatness and uncompromising in its comfort.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/5486a2a5-c43c-4fe9-b6f3-859b06bb2a3a/jordan-point-lane-shoes-D1Lvl6.png'),
(2282, 'Nike React Vision', 'No matter where your explorations take you, the Nike React Vision is ready with undeniable style and surreal comfort. Layered textures, durable synthetic leather and reflective design details come together for a sturdy construction that helps you face harsh conditions. Plus, React foam and a padded tongue help provide cushioning for all your adventures.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/320e2b59-cd95-441a-a6c0-73f927c39454/react-vision-shoes-8pkNK3.png'),
(2283, 'Nike Victori One', 'From the beach to the stands, the Victori One is a must-have slide for everyday activities. Subtle yet substantial updates like a wider strap and softer foam make lounging easy. Go ahead—enjoy endless comfort for your feet.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/77874acd-bf25-4037-bf21-9b442d1b28eb/victori-one-slides-3V75Sf.png'),
(2284, 'Air Jordan 1 Mid', 'Inspired by the original AJ1, this mid-top edition maintains the iconic look you love while choice colours and crisp leather give it a distinct identity.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/514cb17e-dd49-4785-bd59-4e9e7bb6a957/air-jordan-1-mid-shoes-qghcm1.png'),
(2285, 'Nike Victori One', 'From the beach to the stands, the Victori One is a must-have slide for everyday activities. Subtle yet substantial updates like a wider strap and softer foam make lounging easy. Go ahead—enjoy endless comfort for your feet.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/b8c72d07-d64e-47f3-88cf-17307963e5a7/victori-one-slides-bV9q47.png'),
(2286, 'Air Jordan 1 Mid', 'Inspired by the original AJ1, this mid-top edition maintains the iconic look you love while choice colours and crisp leather give it a distinct identity.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/0d265602-b5fa-46c1-8eb6-b3e56c7f52b9/air-jordan-1-mid-shoes-LhVk3g.png'),
(2287, 'Nike Air Max 95 Next Nature', 'Taking inspiration from the human body and \'90s athletics style, the Air Max 95 Next Nature mixes unbelievable comfort with a head-turning look. The wavy side panels add a natural flow to any outfit while visible Air units in the heel and forefoot deliver soft, responsive cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/b0803938-401e-4728-8c26-dafd1c7ea1ee/air-max-95-next-nature-shoes-DKsDNr.png'),
(2288, 'Nike Air VaporMax 2021 FK', 'Made from at least 20% recycled materials by weight, the Nike Air VaporMax 2021 FK is airy and easy to wear with super-stretchy Flyknit fabric (plus a soft collar that sculpts your ankle). The stitched-on Swoosh and recycled TPU heel clip add a splash of intrigue as you float down the streets on incredibly soft VaporMax cushioning.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/6b7918cc-f111-42ae-862a-e37b8d3ead6b/air-vapormax-2021-fk-shoes-StNqnL.png'),
(2289, 'Nike Air Max 95 By You', 'Celebrate workwear\'s wide appeal with a new take on the Nike Air Max 95 By You. Utilitarian materials like polished twill and leather are rugged and durable with an undeniable nod to runway style. Perfectly understated details like contrast stitching and gradient layers add a new level of depth to this long-time favourite.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1280_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/67d7f342-77eb-4a09-baf6-0fadfe02d57d/custom-nike-air-max-95-by-you.png'),
(2290, 'Nike ACG Air Zoom Gaiadome GORE-TEX', 'Warning: this boot will take you places.Forged from heavy-duty materials, they include GORE-TEX technology and large lugs finely tuned to steep mountain slopes.Put simply, they\'re specifically designed for whatever you want to do out there—hike, backpack or simply explore.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/de5054d7-e58a-4cc5-bf83-3ce5e89ceb79/acg-air-zoom-gaiadome-gore-tex-shoes-34L414.png'),
(2291, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'Nike\'s first lifestyle Air Max brings you style, comfort and big attitude in the Nike Air Max 270. The design draws inspiration from Air Max icons, showcasing Nike\'s greatest innovation with its large window and fresh array of colours.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/awjogtdnqxniqqk0wpgf/air-max-270-shoes-tX4fTb.png'),
(2292, 'Nike P-6000', 'The Nike P-6000 draws on the 2006 Nike Air Pegasus, bringing you a mash-up of iconic style that\'s breathable, comfortable and evocative of that early-2000s vibe.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/947e8e73-8531-4c9f-ad8c-84e0b8584284/p-6000-shoe-Xvx7mk.png'),
(2293, 'Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT 2', 'Premium suede and Jordan Brand\'s signature Formula 23 foam come together to give you an extra luxurious (and extra cosy) AJ1. You don\'t need to play \"either or\" when it comes to choosing style or comfort with this one—which is nice, \'cause you deserve both.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco,u_126ab356-44d8-4a06-89b4-fcdcc8df0245,c_scale,fl_relative,w_1.0,h_1.0,fl_layer_apply/b08506f0-c52c-438d-80de-980655c3a10b/air-jordan-1-zoom-cmft-2-shoes-3bDxbX.png'),
(2294, 'Nike Air Alpha Force 88', 'Step into the \'80s with the Air Alpha Force. Complete with a customisable strap, the throwback style looks just as good on the court as it does on the street.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/4b883e11-d87e-45d9-ba26-8a28a010ebba/air-alpha-force-88-shoes-6RjTrt.png'),
(2295, 'Nike x MMW 005', 'Alyx founder and creative director Matthew M. Williams is known for his ability to push fashion into new spaces. His ethos is simple—combine the influence of his life in New York and California with the latest innovations. The Nike x MMW 005 runs with that idea, bringing you a slide designed to take you to the yoga mat and beyond.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/dd3fa608-e59b-47ad-96ff-9a14b2f6f5c6/mmw-005-slides-0XJFQD.png'),
(2296, 'Nike Dunk High By You', 'Take a seat at the table and add your special touch to the hoops-to-streets icon. Inspired by the outdoors, the customisable design lets you be as expressive as you want. Choose between canvas and suede accents for a healthy dose of trail-time flavour. Add classic leather for those on-the-town days. Next, write a piece of your story on the pull tab, which doubles as the perfect spot to attach your kicks to your backpack when it\'s time to cross streams or hit the beach. Plus, countless colour options let you be as adventurous as you want. Whatever you choose, your influence on the Nike Dunk High is undeniable.', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1280_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/99486859-0ff3-46b4-949b-2d16af2ad421/custom-nike-dunk-high-by-you-shoes.png'),
(2297, 'Dunk Low', 'Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the \'80s icon returns with classic details and throwback hoops flair. Layers of leather and textiles go green in natural olive hues, making these Dunks your must-have seasonal sidekicks. The final touch? A padded, low-cut collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.\nSKU: FB8895-300', 'https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_prod_ss/w_640,c_limit,f_auto/3bd3761d-3c98-4ac4-b503-0969a7072154/nike-dunk-low-oil-green-and-olive-aura-fb8895-300-release-date.jpg'),
(2310, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'The first Air Force 1s were produced in 1982 and were the first basketball shoe to use the Nike Air bubble. Little has been changed, taken away or added to the AF1 since its first release even though over 1,700 colourways have been produced and Nike restrict the sale of the shoe to selected retailers around the world. This clean white leather version features the usual perf toe and wrap around Swoosh branding, a mesh lining and further Nike branding on the tongue and midsole plus a metal AF1 lace jewel.', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_030664_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2311, 'Nike x NOCTA Air Force 1 Low \'Love You Forever\'', 'The Nike x NOCTA collaboration continues as Drake gets his hands on the Air Force 1 Low for a \'Certified Lover Boy\' revamp. Born in \'82, the Air Force 1 is one of the OG in the vast Air lineage, and its simple build has always been a canvas for creativity. Premium tumbled leather features on this one, joined by tonal Swooshing and co-branding on the tongue, heel and insole. Silver lace jewels add a luxe touch, while the white colourway carries on to the tough rubber soles. These are injected with Air technology and feature a grippy tread underfoot. Tonal \'Love you forever\' lettering sits on the heel of the lateral side of the soles for a personalised Drake finish. | CZ8065-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_651044_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2312, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Helmed by Peter Moore, the Nike Dunk Low, a courtside classic from the mid-80s returns in a \'Deep Jungle\' Split guise. Tumbled leather sets up the base with the usual perforations decorating the toe box and insignias on the laterals delivering a touch of heritage. Groundwork-wise, rubber coats the sole unit providing the perfect grip on and off the court. | FB8896-300', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680009_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2313, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Making a name for itself over the past few years, Peter Moore\'s Nike Dunk silhouette has become a streetwear cult classic. With its original design cues, the latest model boasts a leather upper in blue with a crisp white base. Swooshes loop around the sidewalls while we see the usual perforations on the toe box offering breathability. Continuing the colour story, underfoot, a blue sole unit provides sticky grip on and off the court. | DV0833-400', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680696_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2314, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'87 QS', 'Some Air Max Ones are more memorable than others - like Nike\'s \'87 \'Quickstrike\' silhouette that was originally released in limited quantities. The uppers consist of white mesh and stubbly suede - with a collage of low-key colours meant to resemble the patchiness of tan lines. Branding is neatly engraved into the tongue and heel while underfoot, a visible chambered Air capsule brings comfort to the sole, and the rubber outsole comes in black this time around with a waffle tread to ensure traction. | FN7200-224', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_686097_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2315, 'Nike Air Force 1 QS', 'The first basketball sneaker to utilise Nike Air tech - and just look at how far it has come since. The AF1 arrives robed in its \'Cacao Wow\' iteration, from heel cap to toe-box - all coated on top of soft suede. Speckles of sand drift poke through the midsole for a fine-grained rustic finish, which finds its way onto the gluey rubber outsole that\'ll keep you stuck down on-and-off the courts. | FQ8901-259', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699508_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2316, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'Originally launched in 1982, the Nike Air Force 1 was the first basketball shoe to house the Nike Air technology and thus revolutionised basketball trainer design. This model is presented in a premium black leather upper with the famous chucky cup sole, swoosh branding on both sides and embossed Air branding on the rear of the sole | 3151220 01', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_047951_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2317, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'The Nike Air Force 1 roster expands with a two-tone black and white iteration. Smooth leather uppers are informed with tonal Swooshes that across the laterals signalling heritage. Perforations decorate the toe box and a metal dubrae adds a touch of premium. As always, a foam midsole offers cloud-like comfort and grippy rubber with the classic pivot tread completes the design. | DV0788-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_620178_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2318, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'Hangul Day\'', 'Celebrating Hangul Day, Nike scatter muted shades across the latest Air Max 1 with nods to the invention of the Korean Alphabet on the heels, footbeds and hang tags. Uppers adopt brown furry suede panels that sit atop a white mesh base. Swooshing informs the sidewalls and toe doubling up on heritage. Groundwork-wise, Tinker Hatfield\'s timeless design sports visible, Air pods through the midsole while tacky tread covers the outsole for traction. | FQ8150-133', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699501_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2319, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 \'Fresh\'', 'Arriving in a white guise, the Nike Air Force 1 \'07 \'Fresh\' updates the classic silhouette with a soft leather construction, which makes it less prone to creasing. Not only that, it\'s also easier to keep your newest pair in prime condition thanks to debossed branding which takes the place of the usual tongue labels. Keeping it monochromatic with a crisp white hue from Swooshes to the laces, the pair comes with perforations in both the sock-liner and toe for breeziness, while a well-cushioned Air midsole adds support via the midsole. Finishing off, grippy rubber signs off with sticky traction through the outsole. | DM0211-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_528642_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2320, 'Nike Air Max 95', 'The covetable Air Max 95 returns, and this time the iteration is constructed with layered suede, tumbled leather and mesh uppers in tonal hues of black. Detailed with subtle branding to the tongue and heel, the silhouette rests above the iconic Air Unit midsole for supreme cushioning in every step. Completing the silhouette is a rubber outsole for tailored traction and support | 609048-092', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_025919_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2321, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 \'Fresh\'', 'Celebrating its 40th anniversary, the Nike Air Force 1 \'07 returns back to the shelves with a bunch of new iterations. This \'Triple Black\' revamp boasts a premium leather on its upper to avoid creases and crinkles, plus there\'s a tonal rubber sole unit underfoot to live up to its title. Air cushioned as always, with every landing you\'ll receive cloud-like comfort, while Swooshing and tongue labelling represent the culture. | DM0211-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_598658_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2322, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Here, we see Tinker Hatfield\'s Air Max 1 clad in a \'Medium Olive\' colourway, with grey, white and green tones making up the majority of the upper. The material choices of mesh with buttery suede and leather emphasizes a premium execution that nods to the original while further down the midsole with visible Air tech offers a responsive ride. A rubber outsole adds grip, and the shoe is completed with lateral Swooshes and a branded patch on the tongue. | FD9082-102', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679854_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2323, 'Nike Cortez - ?exclusive', 'We\'ve gone against the grain for this latest ?exclusive, bringing richer, more earthy tones to this Bill Bowerman classic from \'72. In terms of the colour, the dark hues take this shoe into a completely different space, offering a different style to opt for than the traditional ones. Suedes combine with premium leathers, while black Swooshes assert their dominance on the sidewalls. Serrated rubber soles hark back to its track function, and orange tones on the insole nod to our brand colours. | FJ5180-200', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_645712_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2324, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Looking back to the archives to the revolutionary Nike Air Mag, inspired by \"Back to the Future Part II\", this iteration of Air Force 1 draws from the iconic colourway. Dressed in leather and ripstop for added durability, the uppers arrive in complete \'Wolf Grey\', aside from crisp white Swooshes and heel tabs. The white theme continues at the cushioned midsole, which is rounded off with the futuristic semi-translucent outsole. As a nod to the Mags, \'Light Aqua\' is added to tongue labels, insoles and AIR lettering. | FV0383-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679956_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2325, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'86', 'You know the winds are up when Nike start layering textures on the Air Max One \'86\'s. This premium edition gets a baby blue suede foundation on its uppers, layered with washed black denim on its laterals, pink for the overlays, and scaled leather for the mudguard. Nike insignias get glossed in neutral detailing on the tongue and heel, rested up by a coconut milk midsole which houses that trademark encapsulated Air. The Swoosh comes stencilled in white, and the rubber outsole has a two-tone waffle tread to sign-off. | FB9647-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699399_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2326, 'Nike Air VaporMax Plus', 'Merging the past and present, Nike\'s Air VaporMax Plus is decked with the bold uppers of the Air Max Plus and the iconic VaporMax outsole. Unveiled in a \"Triple Black\" colourway, the silhouette\'s nylon uppers work in harmony with the lace cage for supportive comfort, and a full-length Air cushioning midsole rests below for premium cushioning. Accented with subtle branding throughout, the exclusive trainer is complete with a bubble outsole for a buoyant feel underfoot | 924453-004 | Also available in female sizes - 10438', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_009090_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2327, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Taking inspiration from the late \'80s, Nike\'s Air Max 1 SC arrives in a calming, wintery uniform. Brushed \'Cool Grey\' suede overlays a white mesh, while premium \'Noise Aqua\' leather laps around the mudguard. The silhouette sits atop an icy white Air Max sole unit with flecked grey, black and aqua grippy rubber tread underfoot. The design is signed off by tumbled white leather Swooshes. | FB9660-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680019_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto');
INSERT INTO `models` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `img_url`) VALUES
(2328, 'Nike Terminator Low', 'A hardwood classic arrives on our shelves with a new low cut twist. The Nike Terminator Low is fitted with a leather base and hairy suede overlays adding a touch of premium to dark toned silhouette. Perforations take their usual spot complemented by Swooshes reinforcing lineage while underfoot, a cushioned midsole offers comfort. The rubber sole features a herringbone traction patterm too - the same as the original from 1985. | FV0396-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679946_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2329, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', 'Gearing up for the autumnal season, Nike\'s AF1 touches down coated in a warm wheat shade across its suede uppers. This low-cut iteration boasts the standard perforated toe box for enhanced breathability, with robust rope laces offering an industrial aesthetic. Underfoot, the shoe\'s encapsulated Air midsole delivers supreme levels of cushioned comfort, and a rubber outsole ensures ultimate grip on and off the court | CJ9179-200', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_334257_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2330, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Come winter-ready with Nike in this pair of Air Force 1s, which have been transformed in ways that will make wet socks a thing of the past. Elements are borrowed from winter boot designs, like a reinforced toe box and ripstop panels, to add durability and protect you against harsher conditions. \'Cargo Khaki\' accents sing out against the \'Phantom\' backdrop of the upper, whilst the speckled \'Phantom\' midsole is highlighted by a speckled \'Cargo Khaki\' outsole to round off the design. FB8877-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679961_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2331, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'Dominating basketball and hip-hop culture worldwide since the \'80s, the Air Force 1 continues to stay original and innovative. Crisp white dominates the upper alongside \'Bronzine\' logos on the tongue and heel to create contrast. Classic branding consists of sidewall Swooshes, while durable rubber soles offer tacky traction and Air cushioning delivers cushioned comfort underfoot. | DV0788-104', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667594_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2332, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 \'Fresh\'', 'A more premium rendition of Bruce Kilgore\'s classic lands - here\'s the grey Nike Air Force 1 \'07 Fresh. This sneaker is still reminiscent of the classic, offering a premium leather upper with the usual slightly chunky silhouette and perforated details. Swooshing blends into the sidewalls too, while the thick rubber sole has spongy Air cushioning comfort - a technology first used on the Tailwind in \'79. | DM0211-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_645708_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2333, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Peter Moore\'s low-cut Dunk gets animated with an \'Anthracite\' colour palette to its two-toned upper offering a lifestyle look and feel to the courtside icon. Combing with reflective accents for contrast, Swooshes loop around the sidewalls while we see the toe set up with usual perforations. Continuing the colour story, underfoot, a grey and blue sole unit provides the perfect grip on and off the court. | FV0384-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680697_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2334, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'After launching in 1987, Tinker Hatfield\'s Air Max 1 has been a pioneer is forward-thinking footwear. This iteration in white is brought to life with bold black mudguards and vibrant \'University Gold\' on the Swoosh, which dances across the sidewalls. Also in white, the midsole adds unrivalled comfort thanks to its visible Air unit at the heel. | FD9082-104', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679855_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2335, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Harking back to Nike\'s 2000 CO.JP concept, the latest Air Max 1 iteration arrives in a \'Michigan\' inspired makeup adopting yellow snake-like patterned panels atop a smooth navy leather base. Swooshing informs the sidewalls taking its grain from the AF1 \'Snakeskin Cocoa\' while embroidered motifs double up on heritage. Groundwork-wise, Tinker Hatfield\'s timeless design sports visible, Air pods through the midsole while tacky tread covers the outsole for traction. | FJ5479-410', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_677912_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2336, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'To celebrate the silhouette\'s 30th anniversary, Nike has treated us to a monochromatic Air Max 90 capsule. Up top, there\'s a few slight tweaks that take it closer to Tinker Hatfield\'s 1990 OG than post-2008 reissues: the mudguard starts lower at the forefoot and rises closer to the collar; the toe box height has also been readjusted to make it slightly narrower; so too has the heel branding\'s shape. What\'s more, extra padding at the ankle serves up plush comfort, taking it one step closer to the original. Downstairs, it\'s business as usual with sole-supporting Air technology to cushion your every step | CN8490-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_341585_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2337, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Readied in a premium \'Olive\' shade, Nike\'s lauded Dunk Low model arrives wrapped in a canvas base with tumbled leather overlays in a dark green tone. Peter Moore\'s design is accompanied by \'Sail\' midsoles that work in tandem with labelling on the tongue. The pair are rounded out with a tacky outsole and Swooshes sitting on the laterals delivering a touch of heritage. | DZ2538-300', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667122_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2338, 'Nike Air Max 95', 'In 1995, Sergio Lozano used the human body as inspiration for his ground-breaking Air Max 95 silhouette. This trainer has muscular leather side panels, and above, skin-like mesh protects the lacing system that is based on a rib cage. Originally built for top-performing athletes, this trainer has maintained supreme comfort, boasting Nike Air cushioning and a foam midsole with comforting flex grooves. What\'s more, Air Max branding is dotted throughout, signalling a classic. | CT1268-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_148464_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2339, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 Pro Tech', 'Nodding to hoop heritage, the latest low-cut rendition from \'82 arrives draped in waterproof leather uppers. Swooshes feature on the sidewalls while embossed perforations layer up on the toe harking to the original Air Force 1\'s design. Underfoot plush Air cushioning provides a comfy ride every time and grippy rubber coats the outsole. | FB8875-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679955_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2340, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'86 OG', 'Where it all started, Nike celebrates the journey of its first Air Max shoe, fully replicating it with the OG details. The first pair to house the visible Air unit - inspired by a trip to the Pompidou in Paris - this pair is utterly retro and fitted with the original \'Big Bubble\'. Classic Swoosh branding and enlarged Air logos signal heritage while uppers are dressed leather and mesh in \'Obsidian\' and \'University Red\' hues. | DQ3989-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_686083_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2341, 'Nike Dunk High', 'Dunk High', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680699_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2342, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'87 QS', 'Denim fans, this one\'s for you. Tinker Hatfield\'s design gets an all-new look with uppers clad in layers of denim, mixing shades of \'Aura\', \'Midnight Navy\' and \'Pale Ivory\'. The 1987 original gets an early 2000s patchwork double-denim reboot with hints of a burnt orange Autumnal hue at the tongue and stitching detail around the mudguard. The \'Sail\' coated midsole unit sits atop a navy outsole, which complements the retro aesthetic. | FQ8900-440', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699506_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2343, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'An all-new muted colour palette dresses this Nike Air Max 1 SC, which comes straight from a 2000s dream. Delicate \'Light Bone\' suede envelopes neutral mesh and textiles uppers, while \'Violet Dust\' settles on the sidewall Swoosh. Premium leather covers the mudguard above the Air Max sole unit, dressed in a crisp white. | FB9660-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680023_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2344, 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07 LV8', 'With it\'s 40th year anniversary in the rear-view mirror, the Air Force 1 is not even close to hitting the brakes. This revamp of the \'07 edition comes loaded with phantom black and creamy coconut leather uppers that build up into a soft meshy tongue. Downstairs, the LV8 lives up to its name and gives the midsole heightened elevation, and a white Swoosh signs things off. | FD2592-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680694_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2345, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Draped in its winter armour, Peter Moore\'s creation gets a cold update for the seasons in premium leather. This iteration sees a white foundation dressed in blue accents, with a mesh tongue and inner lining that brings comfort alongside warmth. Nike branding adorns the tongue and heel cap, while all of the above sits atop a cushioned white midsole and royal blue rubber outsole that\'ll keep you gripped down to the ground; ice or no ice. | FQ8826-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680698_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2346, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'A deliciously vintage take on the Dunk Low with Nike\'s \'Bronzine and Sesame\' iteration. Transitioning between desert-toned colours throughout its leather uppers, the texture changes between fuzzy for its overlays including the Swoosh and worn-out for its base foundations. Picante red accents do the honours for the branding, tongue, laces, and padded ankle collar - the last of which has a homey quilted aesthetic that embellishes that vintage feel. | FQ8897-252', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699504_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2347, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low Premium', 'Late autumnal look here from Nike with this premium \'07 inspired instalment into the Air Force 1 lineage. Showcasing an ale brown and midnight navy colourway, its uppers are made from a collage of warm tweed and cosy corduroy fabrics. All of the legendary hallmarks of its \'80s origins mostly remain - with its off-white foam midsole and trademark Nike Air cushioning. A corduroy Swoosh sews this silhouette into premium sneaker territory. | FQ8744-410', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679949_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2348, 'Nike P-6000', 'Here we have the Nike P-6000. Nike\'s runner was inspired by the brand\'s famous Pegasus silhouette, which was introduced way back in 1983 for the everyday runner. Handpicking elements from later versions of the Pegasus - namely the Pegasus 25 and the 2006 - the multi-layered shoe is panelled with a combination of sturdy leather and breathable mesh. Dipped in glossy accents throughout, the runner also features Cushlon foam technology underfoot. If you\'re unfamiliar with this fantastic tech, Cushlon is made from a mix of supportive phylon and rubber additives, which makes the midsole lightweight, buoyant and highly responsive to your every step | BV1021-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_156633_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2349, 'Nike Cortez', 'The Cortez debuted in \'72 as the first ever Nike shoe to display the Swoosh, and, well, you know the rest. Inspired by the firs that dwell outside the Nike World Headquarters, this iteration of the Cortez gets coated in coniferous green uppers wrapped from leather, suede and canvas. Contrasting accents and branding keep it grounded in the same colour-blocking aesthetic as the OG - while a springy midsole absorbs impact and provides snugness. Classic serrated rubber all-purpose soles polish of the shoe with solid grip that\'s ready for the track or the streets. | DZ2795-300', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680122_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2350, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Clean addition to the Air Max 1 register that arrives in a \'University Blue\' colourway which is often correlated with Michael Jordan\'s college days. Complimenting the blue, this crisp silhouette is made from white mesh and grey suede uppers with Nike Air Max branding on the heel and tongue tab. A black and white waffled sole finishes things on the bottom, and this Air Max 1 gets signed off by a calm blue Swoosh. | FD9082-103', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679856_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2351, 'Nike Cortez', 'Joining the \'Athletic Department\' collection is the Cortez that\'s presented with a full suede upper in \'Pale Ivory\'. Vintage branding sits on the tongue tab while footbeds hark to the shoe\'s \'72 origins. Swooshes assert their dominance on the sidewalls looping around to the heel in \'Deep Royal Blue\' for contrast while further down a see-saw sole is fitted with gum rubber for a retro finish. | FQ8108-110', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680120_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2352, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Here, we see Tinker Hatfield\'s Nike Air Max 1 adopt the similar colour blocking to the \'Chili\' from 2003. White mesh sets up the base this time around with light grey suede overlays covering the uppers. Red sidewall Swooshes and a branded tongue patch nod to lineage while further down the midsole with visible Air tech offers a responsive ride and a rubber Waffle outsole adds grip to each step. | FD9082-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_666807_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2353, 'Nike Dunk Remastered', 'The lauded Nike Dunk Low gets an off-court setup on this white and black Remastered release. Souped-up and technical, this one arrives with mesh and leather uppers and a reworked foam tongue. Groundwork-wise, rubber coats the sole unit providing the perfect grip on and off the court. | DV0821-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_668425_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2354, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Helmed by Peter Moore, the Nike Dunk Low, a courtside classic from the mid-80s returns in a black and yellow pairing, indulging in the iconic \'Panda\' paint up. Tumbled leather sets up the base with the usual perforations decorating the toe box and insignias on the laterals delivering a touch of heritage. Groundwork-wise, rubber coats the sole unit providing the perfect grip on and off the court. | FQ2431-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667686_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2355, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Since it first graced the NBA basketball courts in 1985, the Peter Moore-designed Nike Dunk has been at the forefront of subcultural trends and streetwear style. The \'Team Gold\' rendering sees the shoe fitted with blocks of titular gold through the uppers, sitting on a crisp white leather base. The two-toned sole is complete with grippy rubber for responsive traction, and to finish, toe box perforations provide ventilation for all-day breathability. | DV0833-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_647155_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2356, 'Nike Zoom Vomero 5', 'Pulled from the archives of 2010, Nike\'s Zoom Vomero 5 is back in a crisp neutral Autumnal palette of olive shades and \'Light Bone\'. This former runner boasts breezy mesh, leather and plastic accents on the upper for a stable but comfortable ride. \'Medium Olive\' injects the Swoosh that crosses the textured sidewall, matching the tongue and inner lining. White cushioned midsoles are intercepted by a flash of \'Neutral Olive\' to complete the silhouette. | FV0397-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680060_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2357, 'Nike Zoom Vomero 5', 'Back from the 2010 archives, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 adds another colour up to the roster with a versatile all-black palette. Formerly a runner, the silhouette boasts breezy mesh, leather and synthetic uppers and plenty of textures, with Swooshes providing unmissable heritage through the sidewalls and springy CushIon cushioning through the midsole. | BV1358-003', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667146_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2358, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'The latest Nike Air Force 1 Low exercises a white leather upper, with red hits featuring on the branded heels, tongues and Swooshes that looping around the sidewalls. This rests on a crisp white and red, Air-injected midsole that complements the shoe\'s palette, and to finish, there is a grippy rubber sole underfoot. | DV0788-102', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667589_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2359, 'Nike Air Max 2 CB 94', 'The Nike Air Max 2 CB 94 returns employing a \'Baroque Brown\' aesthetic. An icon from Nike\'s basketball arsenal, the high-rising shoe sports a leather base with nubuck overlays. Breathable mesh accents the tongue alongside Nike labelling whilst further down we see Air Max cushioning in the form of an Air bubble. To finish, grippy rubber coats the outsole for optimum grip on and off the court. | FJ7013-200', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680083_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2360, 'Nike Air Max 1 \'Urawa\'', 'Designed to pay homage to J League Football Club, Urawa Dragons, the \'Urawa\' first debuted in 2004. The sequel arrives almost 20 years later with \'Pure Platinum\' leather overlays and black mesh uppers. The Swoosh wraps the sidewalls, and the Urawa Dragon logo marks the heel in subtle stitching. The visible Air-tech adds a hint of red to the design - that we saw on the original - and offers cushioning underfoot. | FD9081-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_672357_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2361, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Get ready for winter with Nike in this pair of AF1s, which have been kitted out to battle the cold. The basketball legend has a new seasonal look, premium leather is mixed with ripstop mid panels and seamlessly bound together for insulation and water-resistance. The silhouette is mainly a tonal \'Medium Ash\', except for a \'Bronzine\' tongue and rubber outsole, which sing out against the dark backdrop. Utility laces finish off this winterised take on Bruce Kilgore\'s shoe. | FB8877-200', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679959_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2362, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'To celebrate the silhouette\'s 30th Anniversary, Nike has treated us to a monochromatic Air Max 90 capsule. Up top, there\'s a few slight tweaks that take it closer to Tinker Hatfield\'s 1990 OG than post-2008 reissues: the mudguard starts lower at the forefoot and rises closer to the collar; the toe box height has also been readjusted to make it slightly narrower; so too has the heel branding\'s shape. What\'s more, extra padding at the ankle serves up plush comfort, taking it one step closer to the original. Downstairs, it\'s business as usual with sole-supporting Air technology to cushion your every step | CN8490-003', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_341587_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2363, 'Nike VaporMax Moc Roam', 'Following on from the debut of the Air VaporMax in 2017, Nike presents its latest iteration fusing the VaporMax sole unit onto the Moc Roam. A black colour palette decorates the textile upper and protective shroud, which covers the inner bootie. Its no-sew design replaces traditional manufacturing with heat-welded overlays that advance rugged wear, while the Max Air system underfoot cushions every step. Branded heels deliver the final flourish. | DZ7273-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680309_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2364, 'Nike Zoom Vomero 5', 'A silhouette which debuted in 2010, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 is back again. The shoe has followed that well-versed transition from a running staple to lifestyle silhouette, and showcases breathable mesh through the uppers, teamed with leather and synthetics which are layered up for lots of structure at the top. Swooshes certify that this one belongs to the Nike family, and further down CushIon technology brings support throughout the midsole. It comes with a grippy finish thanks to rubber through the outsole, plus it has shallow lugs to really optimise traction. | FJ4151-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667147_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2365, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low \'07 LX', 'This version of Bruce Kilgore\'s basketball design has a tumbled earthy feel, just in time for Autumn. The dark green hue of \'Sequoia\' sweeps across the smooth leather and canvas of the upper, while \'Light Orewood Brown\' decorates the buttery suede Swoosh and the entire sole unit. Air cushioning lines the midsole to add a spring in your step on the courts or out in nature. | DV7186-301', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667069_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2366, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'The archetypal Nike Air Max 1 returns with a \'Royal Blue\' remodeling; this release boasts hues of white, grey, and blue across its premium mesh and suede uppers. Sidewall Swooshes and branding touches confirm Beaverton legacy while an Air Max unit is in the heel of a crisp white midsole, defining this classic design\'s elite comfort. A contrasting black outsole offers a grippy finish. | FD9082-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_666821_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2367, 'Nike Cortez', 'Nike utilizes the Cortez\'s original tooling from \'72, combining shimmery textile uppers with premium suede overlays. In terms of the colour, the bright yellow hues take this shoe into a completely different space, offering a different style to opt for than the traditional ones. Navy Swooshes assert their dominance on the sidewalls while serrated rubber soles hark back to its track function. | DZ2795-700', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667118_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2368, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Peter Moore\'s creation reaches new heights with this iconic Dunk Low silhouette. Since its debut in \'85 the Nike Dunk has evolved yearly from its basketball roots - now a timeless streetwear staple. This time its uppers consist of a well-patched mix of corduroy and tweed materials dressed in an ale brown and midnight blue colourway, which brings a changing of the seasons feel to it. A padded collar nods to the OG model, and its Swoosh is signed off by a corduroy signature. | FQ8746-410__', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679998_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2369, 'Nike Terminator Low', 'Travelling back to the 1980s, Nike bring back a beloved classic from the archives - the Terminator Low. Hailing from the Golden Era of basketball, this icon returns, sporting a \'Phantom\' and black colourway. Croc-embossed leather coats the Swoosh and overlays, which accentuate the perforated toe box, before meandering in waves around the tongue. Cushioned midsoles are given a vintage look in an off-white huge, while the design is rounded off by \'NIKE\' branding to the heels. Relive the glory days with this revived silhouette. | FQ8127-030', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679948_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2370, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Just in time for the Autumn/Winter, Nike present an essential addition to the Dunk Low family. This tonal iteration comes in shades of \'Burgundy Crush\' and consists of a premium twill upper with soft suede overlays. The soft leather Swoosh is highlighted against the sidewall in a lighter hue of the burgundy uniform. The rubber midsole completes this warm wintery silhouette with Air cushioning that offers all-day comfort | FB8895-600', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_681630_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2371, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'Air Force 1 Low', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_686110_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2372, 'Nike Cortez', 'Released in \'72, the Cortez was one of Nike\'s co-founder Bill Bowerman\'s running innovations. Embraced at the Olympics and across cultures over the globe, the shoe\'s storied history makes it a perennial classic. Anchored here with navy leather uppers, contrasting Swooshes assert their dominance on the medial and laterals signaling heritage. Beneath, the serrated rubber soles hark back to its track function. | DM4044-400', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_645720_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2373, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Drenched in sporting heritage, the Nike Dunk Low is a silhouette that just keeps giving. _Premium leather features on the upper of this one, with a white base and navy hues adding a contrast. Perforations on the toe box keep things breathable while stitched Swooshes loop around the sides. Sturdy rubber soles carry the upper with cushioning injected into the midsoles. | DV0831-104', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_668426_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2374, 'Nike Air Max 97', 'Sporting bold hues of black from head-to-toe, this iteration of the rippled Air Max 97 delivers comfort with its textured and leather uppers. A signature Swoosh highlights the sidewalls, while an Air-injected sole unit promises unrivalled support underfoot. A dependable traction outsole is positioned on the underside to sign the covetable the style off | BQ4567-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_088627_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2375, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low \'Colour of the Month\'', 'Another AF1 from its \'Colour of the Month\' series - which is showing no signs of coming to an end, we\'re pleased to say. With this iteration we are graced with white leather and synthetic uppers, with the Swoosh and Nike branding accents given the gum treatment. Its basketball origins ring true with its Air cushioned sole that adds the final touch. | FN5924103', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679950_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2376, 'Nike Cortez', 'Released in \'72, the Cortez was one of Nike\'s co-founder Bill Bowerman\'s running innovations. Embraced at the Olympics and across cultures over the globe, the shoe\'s storied history makes it a perennial classic. Anchored here with black textile and leather uppers, contrasting Swooshes assert their dominance on the medial and laterals signaling heritage. Beneath, the serrated rubber soles hark back to its track function. | DZ2795-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667090_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2377, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'The Nike Air Max 1 is a piece of sneaker heritage and one of Tinker Hatfield\'s finest works for the Beaverton label. This future-proof silhouette first landed in \'87, standing as the first to represent an exposed Air unit in the sole - this was inspired by a deconstructed bit of architecture in Paris. Now, the shoe opts for bronze and creamy hues on the upper, with suede and mesh playing host to classic Swooshing. As always, visible Air units provide plush comfort and that legendary Nike look - three decades old and still going strong. | DZ4549-110', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667125_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2378, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Celebrating \'Hangul Day\', Nike scatter muted shades across the Dunk Low with nods to the invention of the Korean Alphabet on the heels and footbeds. Uppers are coated in premium layers of leather adjoined by sidewall Swooshes and toe box perforations. Further down, cushioned midsoles offer comfort in every stride and gum rubber soles compliment the uppers colour palette, keeping your step as sturdy as ever. | FQ8147-104', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_699499_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2379, 'Nike Air Humara', 'The outdoor-apt Nike Air Humara returns to the shelves with an authentic trail aesthetic and a must-have black and metallic silver colourway. Stripes of exposed stitched leather wraps around mesh on this one, while dark tones fill every segment. Heel and tongue pulls add some functionality too, and textured midsoles and really grippy treads gift you with confidence on unpredictable landscapes. | FJ7098-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_677902_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2380, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'It doesn\'t get more iconic than the Nike Air Force 1, a silhouette with a grand title named after the President\'s personal aeroplane; a title that links to the elevation that these shoes provided on the basketball courts. Arriving in a white colourway with hits of blue, leather uppers inform the build with Swooshes landing on the sidewalls. An Air-cushioned midsole provides renowned comfort and a grippy outsole provides an advantage on the courts. | FV0383-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680692_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2381, 'Nike Terminator Low', 'Pulling inspiration from the \'Be True To Your School\' ad, the Nike Terminator Low arrives executed with one of the original colourways released in \'85 - \'Georgetown\'. Premium leather sets up the base offset with navy overlays. Perforations take their usual spot complemented by Swooshes reinforcing lineage and Nike lettering sits at the heels. Underfoot, a cushioned midsole offers comfort and tacky rubber brings traction. | FN6830-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_666994_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2382, 'Nike Air Max 1', 'Released in \'87, for the Nike Air Max 1, Tinker Hatfield had the vision of creating a visible Air unit after visiting the Centre Pompidou in Paris. This complexly put together building simply has nothing to hide, and this design ethos is replicated on the visible Air unit that has travelled through the decades since. Now arriving with a Premium guise, the shoe gets a natural array of colours across wraps of leather and nubuck. The silhouette remains the same, while the Air units signal effortless, long-lasting comfort throughout wear. | FB5060-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_645966_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2383, 'Nike VaporMax Moc Roam', 'Following on from the debut of the Air VaporMax in 2017, Nike presents its latest iteration fusing the VaporMax sole unit onto the Moc Roam. The \'Coconut Milk\' colour palette decorates the textile upper and protective shroud, which covers the inner bootie. Its no-sew design replaces traditional manufacturing with heat-welded overlays that advance rugged wear, while the Max Air system underfoot cushions every step. Branded heels deliver the final flourish. | DZ7273-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680036_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2384, 'Nike Killshot 2 Leather', 'First reintroduced in 2012, the Nike Killshot 2 was inspired by the original low-profile 1979 tennis shoe. The silhouette is made up of a combination of textures, from smooth suede accents and premium leather uppers to bouncy gum soles and shiny leather Swooshes. This pair offers a fuss free statement that looks great courtside and beyond. | 432997-121', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680016_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2385, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'The latest Nike Air Force 1 Low arrives with waterproof tooling offering a rain-ready fit to this low-cut rendition. On the uppers, white leather coats the uppers while \'University Gold\' Swooshes feature on the sidewalls, looping around to Air branding on the heel. The top sits on an Air-injected midsole that complements the shoe\'s palette, and to finish, there is a grippy, gum rubber sole underfoot. | FD7039-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_677900_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2386, 'Nike Zoom Vomero 5', 'Back from the 2010 archives, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 adds another colour up to the roster with a \'Vast Grey\' palette. Formerly a runner, the silhouette boasts breezy mesh, leather and synthetic uppers and plenty of textures, with Swooshes providing unmissable heritage through the sidewalls and springy Zoom Air cushioning through the midsole. | BV1358-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_157067_b?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2387, 'Nike Air Max Scorpion', 'The Air Max lineage evolves with Nike\'s latest Air Max Scorpion offering arriving in a black paint-up. Up top, snug, techy Flyknit uppers are met with a lacing system while Swooshes adorn the medial and lateral sides. This shoe has been tried and tested in the Nike Sports Research Lab and has utilised 3D VR design software and engineering tools, with morphology data and pressure maps. It\'s inspired by the concept of \'point loading\' with injected Air cushioning and an elevated sole unit for responsiveness, this silhouette showcases the label\'s revolutionary innovation. | DJ4701-003 | This product is made with at least 20% recycled content by weight', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_598949_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2388, 'Nike Air Max 95', 'Nike\'s Sergio Lozano-designed Air Max 95 returns this season in an a \'Black Earth\' colouring, perfect for your rotation all-year-round. Inspired by the human anatomy, this silhouette has layered suede and textile uppers with techy mesh and a super-fast lacing system. Subtle Swooshes adorn the heels, while Air Max tongue branding signals its cushioning technology below. What\'s more, the full-length Air unit in the sole is visible, offering an insight into the design processes. | FD0652-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_620325_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2389, 'Nike Terminator Low', 'Nike revisits its basketball-rooted catalogue with the newest low-profile iteration of the Terminator Low. The \'85 silhouette arrives with a leather base with croc-textured suede overlays adding a touch of premium. Perforations take their usual spot complemented by Swooshes reinforcing lineage while underfoot, a cushioned midsole offers comfort and tacky rubber brings traction. | FN7815-200', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_666992_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2390, 'Nike Air Footscape Woven', 'The Nike Air Footscape revives itself with a \'White Cow\' iteration - doing its \'90s predecessor justice by maintaining its comfort-focussed aesthetic. Ergonomic in its design, this classic embodies cow-patterned horsehair leather and faux fur with woven sidewalls and offset laces. Down below, everything sits atop a cushioned midsole, and a rubber outsole ensures grip underneath. Nike insignias are displayed on the tongue, heel and sole. | FB1959102', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680128_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2391, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low \'07 LX', 'The more premium LX Nike Air Force 1 \'07 gets a \'Command Force\' guise this season. A vintage silhouette from \'82, this sneaker still looks fresh today, standing tall as one of the greatest Nike releases from the Air lineage. This shoe first cut its teeth on the hardwood courts, while its impact on sub-culture and sneaker culture is somewhat unparalleled. Throughout this time, the Air Force 1 has maintained its Air cushioned sole - this is in the mid region and offers a cloud-like sponginess throughout wear, you\'ve got to try it. | DR0148-102', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_645956_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2392, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'A change up from the usual material composition here for the iconic Nike shoe. The Air Force 1 \'07 LX Low \'Team Gold\' swaps out leather base for canvas, with titular golden overlays in a soft, tumbled leather for that premium feel. Black Swooshing sweeps across the sidewalls, joined by branding at the tongue and heel for a nod to Beaverton origins. Air cushioning runs through the midsole of the design from \'82, sitting atop grippy rubber soles below. | DV7186-700', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_647147_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2393, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'A starry night collides with the Air Force 1 - and the rest is history. Everything that made the \'80s construction so loved is echoed in this silhouette, with a crisp white leather upper and Air technology hidden throughout the sole. Electric blue Nike Air Force 1 branding sits on the tongue and heel, while the Swoosh and accents come in black leather and are dashed with constellatory accents. | FV6656-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679957_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2394, 'Nike Air Force 1 LV8', 'Air Force 1 LV8', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680695_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2395, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Making a name for itself over the past few years, Peter Moore\'s Nike Dunk silhouette has become a streetwear cult classic. The latest iteration harks back to the \'Syracuse\' that was originally released as a part of the \'Be True To Your School\' series, nodding to universities playing in Dunks. With its original design cues, the latest model boasts a leather upper in orange with a crisp white base. Cracked Swooshes loop around the sidewalls while we see the usual perforations on the toe box offering breathability. Continuing the colour story, underfoot, an orange sole unit provides sticky grip on and off the court. | FN7773-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667189_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2396, 'Nike Dunk High', 'Crisp and classic, the Nike Dunk High has received a panda-like \'White/Black\' guise across its smooth leather upper. Arriving with sturdy rubber soles, toe box perforations and signature Swooshing, this high-top rendition is a must-have for your collection. | DD1399-105', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_457704_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2397, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Peter Moore\'s design comes with a premium execution and classic colour up for this latest release. The Nike Dunk Low \'Clear Jade\' arrives with a quintessential green and white colour blocking, with a smooth leather base Swooshes across the sidewalls. Perforations through the toe box provide a breezy feel, and grippy rubber maintains reliable traction underfoot. | DV0833-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667688_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2398, 'Nike Zoom Vomero 5', 'Back from the 2010 archives, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 adds another colour up to the roster with a \'Anthracite\' palette. Formerly a runner, the silhouette boasts breezy mesh, leather and synthetic uppers and plenty of textures, with Swooshes providing unmissable heritage through the sidewalls and springy Zoom Air cushioning through the midsole. | BV1358-002', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_157058_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2399, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'The AF1 arrives in its winter clothing. Up top, it\'s business as usual with a full leather upper, mesh tongue and inner liner. This silhouette incorporates a white foundation, with shaded blue overlays that give it a frosty touch. Nike Air branding is displayed on the tongue and heel cap, with a sleek grey Swoosh on the laterals. Below, a white AF1 midsole sits above a royal blue rubber outsole, which is bolstered by that Nike Air-Sole technology that everybody knows and loves. | FQ8825-100', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_679958_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2400, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low', 'Looking forwards to the colder months, Nike\'s Air Force 1 Low favours a darker arrangement up top with a greyscale leather base and suede overlays. Classic branding consists of sidewall Swooshes, plus tongue and heel insignias while durable rubber soles offer tacky traction and Air cushioning delivers cushioned comfort underfoot. | CW7584-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667578_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2401, 'Nike Lebron XXI', 'Adored by basketball and sneaker enthusiasts alike, the Lebron XXI gets dripped in Lakers colours. An advanced design that combines style and performance, its uppers consist of engineered purple mesh with black suede overlays that work its way around a scintillating lateral Swoosh. \'XX\' branding on the heel tabs features in metallic gold, while the midsole is cushioned by Air Zoom tech. A sunny yellow rubber outsole finalises this Lebron in true LA style. | DR8784-500', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680144_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2402, 'Nike Killshot 2 Leather', 'The Killshot 2 was inspired by Nike\'s original low-profile tennis shoe, reflected in its no-fuss silhouette and gum sole. The cream leather uppers are complemented by soft suede accents to the toe, heels and tongue, while a cream leather Swoosh subtly decorates the sidewall. \'NIKE\' branding on the heel adds a slice of heritage - this one\'s a style that looks good on and off the court. | 432997-128', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680018_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2403, 'Nike Air Force 1 Low \'Colour of the Month\'', 'Continuing to celebrate over 40 years of legacy, Nike presents the Air Force 1 Low Retro \'Colour of the Month\' made with a traditional leather construction in white. Jewel-like Swooshes get swapped out for green leather on the sidewalls while a gum rubber sole offers court-ready traction. | FD7039-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_686066_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2404, 'Nike Cortez', 'Released in \'72, the Cortez was one of Nike\'s co-founder Bill Bowerman\'s running innovations. Embraced at the Olympics and across cultures over the globe, the shoe\'s storied history makes it a perennial classic. For its latest appearance, \'Midnight Navy\' nylon and suede uppers rest on the serrated rubber soles that hark back to its track function. Contrasting white Swooshes envelope the design with final branded touches to the tongue and lacing dubrae. | DZ2795-400', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667107_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2405, 'Nike Air Force 1 Mid \'07', 'Nike - Air Force 1 Mid \'07 - Brown - DJ9158-200,', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_474142_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2406, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'With its original design cues, the latest Dunk model boasts a leather upper in a \'Campfire Orange\' with a crisp white base that plays host to star sprangled Swooshes on the sidewalls. We see the usual perforations on the toe box offering breathability and continuing the colour story, underfoot, a black sole unit provides sticky grip on and off the court. | FV6909-800', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_680011_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2407, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'Peter Moore\'s iconic silhouette is the subject of this latest remastering from the Beaverton label. The Nike Dunk Low comes with additional orange Swooshing to the toe, with its usual smooth leather overlays and a well-padded tongue for comfort throughout wear. The black and white setup is breathable thanks to perforations to the toe, whilst a grippy rubber sole unit which adds plenty of traction to the setup. | FN7808-001', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_668428_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2408, 'Nike Dunk High', 'Dunk High', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_647157_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2409, 'Nike Dunk Low Remastered', 'The Nike Dunk Low gets an off-court setup on this \'Mushroom\' Remastered release. Souped-up and technical, this one arrives with mesh and leather uppers and a reworked foam tongue. Groundwork-wise, rubber coats the sole unit providing the perfect grip on and off the court. | DV0821-101', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/sz_667694_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=580&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2457, 'Nike Dunk Low', 'The \'85 icon is back with these men\'s Dunk Low Retro sneakers from Nike. Keeping the OG design lines inspired by college basketball, these low-profile kicks have a premium leather upper in a classic Black and White colourway. They feature a secure lace up fastening, a padded ankle collar and are sat on a soft foam midsole for supreme cushioning. Created for the hardwood but evolved for the streets, these trainers are finished with signature Nike branding and the iconic Swoosh logo to the sidewalls. Please Note: This item is limited to one per person.', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/jd_391425_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=531&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2458, 'Nike Air Max 95 Ultra', 'Lighter than ever before, lace up in JD-exclusive style with these men\'s Air Max 95 Ultra trainers from Nike. In a Cool Grey and Black colourway, these special edition sneakers have a smooth mesh and synthetic upper, paired with a durable foam midsole and visible Air units in the heel and forefoot. They feature a streamlined lace fastening and padded ankle collar. Finished off with a textured rubber outsole and signature Swoosh Air Max branding.', 'https://i8.amplience.net/i/jpl/jd_681440_a?qlt=92&w=750&h=531&v=1&fmt=auto'),
(2459, 'Nike Air Max Invigor', 'Get ready to dominate your next workout with the Nike Air Max Invigor trainers. These low-top kicks feature breathable technical uppers that keep your feet cool and comfortable during even the most intense gym sessions.\nEach step is expertly cushioned by the foam midsoles and visible Max Air units, providing energy absorption and support. The synthetic soles feature deep treads to provide the best traction, while the graduated sides add style.\nLace up and secure your feet with the lace fastenings and padded ankle collars for extra support. The Nike Swoosh motifs on the sides and tongues and Nike Air branding on the heels add a touch of iconic flair to your look. Perfect for any season or occasion, these trainers are a must-have for any active adventurer looking to take their training to the next level.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12126140_l_a1.jpg'),
(2460, 'Nike Air Max Invigor', 'Get ready to dominate your next workout with the Nike Air Max Invigor trainers. These low-top kicks feature breathable technical uppers that keep your feet cool and comfortable during even the most intense gym sessions.\nEach step is expertly cushioned by the foam midsoles and visible Max Air units, providing energy absorption and support. The synthetic soles feature deep treads to provide the best traction, while the graduated sides add style.\nLace up and secure your feet with the lace fastenings and padded ankle collars for extra support. The Nike Swoosh motifs on the sides and tongues and Nike Air branding on the heels add a touch of iconic flair to your look. Perfect for any season or occasion, these trainers are a must-have for any active adventurer looking to take their training to the next level.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12126140_l_a1.jpg'),
(2461, 'Nike Pegasus', 'The Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 GORE-TEX Men\'s Waterproof Trail Running Shoes are perfect for the next time you hit the trails, crafted with a Gore-Tex layer to keep you protected from the elements, while a lightweight rubber outsole offers a smooth transition from road to trail while still keeping the full length React midsole for a comfortable and responsive feel. Designed with a generative traction pattern to give a fantastic grip on a wide range of surfaces, the design is complete with a colourful design and the classic Nike Swoosh branding.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/21300503_l_a1.jpg'),
(2462, 'Nike Air Max Invigor', 'Get ready to dominate your next workout with the Nike Air Max Invigor trainers. These low-top kicks feature breathable technical uppers that keep your feet cool and comfortable during even the most intense gym sessions.\nEach step is expertly cushioned by the foam midsoles and visible Max Air units, providing energy absorption and support. The synthetic soles feature deep treads to provide the best traction, while the graduated sides add style.\nLace up and secure your feet with the lace fastenings and padded ankle collars for extra support. The Nike Swoosh motifs on the sides and tongues and Nike Air branding on the heels add a touch of iconic flair to your look. Perfect for any season or occasion, these trainers are a must-have for any active adventurer looking to take their training to the next level.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12126140_l_a1.jpg'),
(2463, 'Nike Vomero', 'The Nike Air Zoom Vomero 16 Men\'s Running Shoe are perfect for the next time you hit the track, featuring a shaped and padded ankle collar teamed with a lace fastening that helps to lock your foot down into the shoe. A lightweight construction teamed with responsive cushioning that gives an explosive energy return that is needed when your trying to smash your personal best, completed with the Nike Swoosh branding to the side.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/21233703_l_a1.jpg'),
(2464, 'Nike Vomero', 'The Nike Air Max Alpha Trainer 5 Men\'s Training Shoes are perfect for hitting your sets at the gym, crafted with Max Air cushioning along with a wide, flat base that gives enhanced stability for lifts. A foam ankle collar provides additional protection for your ankle and a lace fastening helps lock your foot down into the shoe, finished off with an enhanced rubber tread pattern for increased traction and the Nike Swoosh branding.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/13120603_l_a1.jpg'),
(2465, 'Nike Air Max SC', 'Experience the perfect fusion of style and performance with the Nike Air Max SC Shoes. Designed for everyday wear, these low-top kicks elevate your outfit to new heights.\nAiry knit and mesh inserts accentuate leather uppers, providing optimum breathability to keep your feet fresh all day. The padded ankle collars offer exceptional support and comfort, while the foam midsoles ensure superior cushioning with every step.\nThe visible Max Air units provide energy absorption and shape retention so you can stay on top of your day. Durable rubber outsoles provide elevated traction, allowing you to conquer the streets with ease. No Nike design is complete without the iconic Swoosh motif on the sides and Nike Air branding on the heels and tongues to let everyone know you\'re a force to be reckoned with.\nInspired by retro styles and made for day-to-day use, the Nike Air Max SC Shoes are the ultimate combination of style and performance. Lace up, embrace the journey, and show the world what you\'re made of!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12102144_l_a1.jpg');
