(2466, 'Nike Revolution', 'Are you at the start of your road running journey? If so, let us introduce you to the Nike Revolution 6 Road Running Shoes, the perfect companions for beginners. Designed with simplicity in mind, these low-top style shoes are packed with features to elevate your performance.\nThe plush mesh upper ensures maximum breathability while the round toes and lace fastenings provide a secure and comfortable fit, and the padded ankle collars surround your feet to provide unparalleled support. The foam midsoles deliver a soft ride, allowing you to conquer any distance with ease and the specially designed outsoles incorporate a natural piston effect for exceptional flexibility and cushioning, ensuring a responsive stride.\nAvailable in multiple colourways, there is a style for every novice. And let\'s not forget the iconic Nike Swoosh on the outer sides, a symbol of excellence, and a sure-fire way to let others know you are wearing the very best.\nLace up and hit the pavement with confidence, knowing that the Nike Revolution 6 Road Running Shoes combine style, comfort, and performance in one. Join the revolution and unleash your inner athlete!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12167703_l_a1.jpg'),
(2467, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'Introducing the Nike Air Max 90 Shoes: The perfect fusion of style and performance inspired by unforgettable 1990s styles. With their classic low-top style and round toes, these airy kicks are designed to make a bold statement wherever you go.\nThe textile uppers, combined with leather and synthetic overlays, offer durability and a sleek look that\'s simply irresistible. Lace fastenings and padded ankle collars ensure a secure and comfortable fit, while the foam midsoles provide lightweight cushioning for maximum comfort during all your athletic adventures.\nBut the real showstopper? The visible Max Air unit in the heel delivers superior cushioning, energy absorption, and shape retention.\nThe Nike Air Max 90 Shoes come in a range of vibrant colourways, while the iconic Swoosh on the sides and Air branding on the heel are symbols of your dedication to style and performance.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12100403_l_a1.jpg'),
(2468, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'Introducing the Nike Court Vision Low Trainers: powerhouses of style and performance. These kicks combine the best of the past and the present, seamlessly merging the classic look of 1980s basketball with fast-paced 21st-century life.\nThis classic silhouette is reimagined for today, cut in a low-top style and crafted in crisp recycled uppers with stitched overlays. Round toes, perforations on the toe boxes and padded low-cut ankle collars and sides offer breathability, keeping your feet cool and comfortable. Traditional lace fastenings deliver a secure fit, while the rubber outsoles with stylised treads ensure superior traction with a stylish twist.\nAvailable in multiple colourways, every pair showcases the iconic Nike Swoosh and the brand\'s signature logo on the tongues and heels, ensuring that everyone around you will know that you are wearing the very best.\nSo, whether you\'re hitting the court or running errands, these Court Vision Low Trainers will elevate your style game while delivering comfort and performance. Channel your inner Michael Jordan and make a statement with every step in these remixed sneakers.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/16105601_l_a1.jpg'),
(2469, 'Nike Pegasus', 'Hit the ground running with Nike\'s Pegasus 40 Road Running Shoes! These powerhouses are here to bring out the best in you and to help you smash your personal best.\nWith their low-top style and single-layer mesh uppers, these shoes provide ultimate breathability to keep your feet cool and comfortable. The round toes and lace fastenings ensure a secure and personalized fit, while the padded ankle collars offer extra cushioning for added support.\nThis pair has neutral support, designed to cater to both heel and forefoot runners. Elsewhere, Nike React technology delivers softer impacts and a responsive ride, giving you the confidence to push your limits. Two Zoom Air units are strategically placed in the forefoot and heel to absorb energy and relieve stress on your muscles, tendons, and joints.\nWith waffle-inspired treads for superior traction and available in multiple styles and colourways, these shoes are perfect for everything from competitive marathons to morning jogs with friends. Get out there and conquer the road with the Nike Pegasus 40 Road Running Shoes!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/21116203_l_a1.jpg'),
