(2500, 'Nike Revolution', 'Refresh your everyday sneaker collection with the Venture Runner Men\'s Trainers from Nike. These shoes have been inspired by running shoes from the 80s and offer a cushioned insole and padded ankle collar for all day comfort. The trainer sits on a bouncy foam midsole for some spring in your step with a durable rubber waffle outsole for plenty of traction and lace closure along the top. There are suede overlays along the upper for long lasting wear and a smarter feel, finished with a steady colour design and classic Nike swoosh branding for the iconic look. Leather upper with leather lining and synthetic sole.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12121040_l_a1.jpg'),
(2501, 'Nike Air Max 97', 'First introduced in 1997 as a technical running shoe, the Air Max 97 Trainers by Nike feature the original ripple design inspired by Japanese bullet trains for an eye-catching aesthetic which has dominated every sneakerheads rotation ever since. The shoes feature a full-length Max Air unit which is integrated in the foam midsole to deliver a springy, soft and responsive feel with every step for incredible all-day comfort and the reflective elements help keep you safe as well as elevating the style in lowlight conditions and the Nike Swoosh branding completes the design.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/11101999_l_a1.jpg'),
(2502, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'The Air Max SYSTM Mens Trainers brought to you by Nike are a great addition to your off duty wardrobe for an on-trend touch, crafted with a low profile ankle collar coupled with a lace fastening for a secure fit, while a cushioned insole and classic Air Max cushioning to the heel ensures comfort with every step. Stitched detailing across the upper along with a tonal panel around the toe gives a stylish touch, finished off with the classic Nike Swoosh branding for true appreciation.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12227403_l_a1.jpg'),
(2503, 'Nike Air Max 90', 'The Men\'s Nike Defy All Day Mens Trainers are a great addition to any casual trainer collection, featuring a lace fastening front with a shaped ankle collar for a secure and comfortable fit with the cushioned insole and moulded outsole provide a comfortable ride, reflective detail increase your visibility and the Nike swoosh branding completes the look.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/13107203_l_a1.jpg'),
(2504, 'Nike Air Max Ivo', 'Inspired by early 90s running shoes from the Beaverton brand. the Air Max IVO trainers from Nike feature a soft foam midsole with a visible air unit on three sides to deliver optimal cushioning and response with every step. The upper includes airy mesh to help keep your feet feeling cool, while the rubber waffle outsole adds heritage styling as well as durable traction and the Nike Swoosh branding adds the finishing touch.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12100540_l_a1.jpg'),
(2505, 'Nike Air Max Ivo', 'Introducing the Nike Court Vision Low Trainers: powerhouses of style and performance. These kicks combine the best of the past and the present, seamlessly merging the classic look of 1980s basketball with fast-paced 21st-century life.\nThis classic silhouette is reimagined for today, cut in a low-top style and crafted in crisp recycled uppers with stitched overlays. Round toes, perforations on the toe boxes and padded low-cut ankle collars and sides offer breathability, keeping your feet cool and comfortable. Traditional lace fastenings deliver a secure fit, while the rubber outsoles with stylised treads ensure superior traction with a stylish twist.\nAvailable in multiple colourways, every pair showcases the iconic Nike Swoosh and the brand\'s signature logo on the tongues and heels, ensuring that everyone around you will know that you are wearing the very best.\nSo, whether you\'re hitting the court or running errands, these Court Vision Low Trainers will elevate your style game while delivering comfort and performance. Channel your inner Michael Jordan and make a statement with every step in these remixed sneakers.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/16105601_l_a1.jpg'),
(2506, 'Nike Air Max Excee', 'Inspired by the unforgettable style of the 1990s, Nike\'s Air Max Excee revisit classic silhouette and bring them into the 21st century in a fusion of fashion and functionality.\nCut in a sleek low-top style, mixed uppers and round toes radiate an effortlessly cool vibe. The lace fastening ensures a secure fit, while the plush ankle collars provide optimal support. The lightweight foam midsole and outsoles offer all-day comfort, so you can stay on your feet and conquer any challenge that comes your way. The visible Air-Sole unit not only adds a stylish touch but also reduces impact, protecting your feet all day every day.\nOf course, the Nike Swooshes on the sides and Nike Air branding on the tongues and heels embody quality and style that has become synonymous with the world-famous brand.\nWith multiple colours and styles available, these kicks allow you to express your unique personality while embracing that vibrant retro spirit.\nSo lace up, turn up the volume on your favourite 90s playlist, and step out in your signature Nike Air Max Excees!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12139946_l_a1.jpg'),
(2507, 'Nike Air Max Excee', 'Refresh your everyday sneaker collection with the Venture Runner Men\'s Trainers from Nike. These shoes have been inspired by running shoes from the 80s and offer a cushioned insole and padded ankle collar for all day comfort. The trainer sits on a bouncy foam midsole for some spring in your step with a durable rubber waffle outsole for plenty of traction and lace closure along the top. There are suede overlays along the upper for long lasting wear and a smarter feel, finished with a steady colour design and classic Nike swoosh branding for the iconic look. Leather upper with leather lining and synthetic sole.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12121040_l_a1.jpg'),
(2508, 'Nike Air Max Excee', 'Introducing the Nike Court Vision Low Trainers: powerhouses of style and performance. These kicks combine the best of the past and the present, seamlessly merging the classic look of 1980s basketball with fast-paced 21st-century life.\nThis classic silhouette is reimagined for today, cut in a low-top style and crafted in crisp recycled uppers with stitched overlays. Round toes, perforations on the toe boxes and padded low-cut ankle collars and sides offer breathability, keeping your feet cool and comfortable. Traditional lace fastenings deliver a secure fit, while the rubber outsoles with stylised treads ensure superior traction with a stylish twist.\nAvailable in multiple colourways, every pair showcases the iconic Nike Swoosh and the brand\'s signature logo on the tongues and heels, ensuring that everyone around you will know that you are wearing the very best.\nSo, whether you\'re hitting the court or running errands, these Court Vision Low Trainers will elevate your style game while delivering comfort and performance. Channel your inner Michael Jordan and make a statement with every step in these remixed sneakers.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/16105601_l_a1.jpg'),
(2509, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'Introducing the Nike Air Max 270 Trainers, the ultimate fusion of style and performance! Packed with features that will have you turning heads, these dynamic kicks will help you dominate your day.\nWith their low-top style and almond toes, they deliver a sleek and modern look that\'s sure to elevate your style game. The woven synthetic and textile uppers- complete with mesh detailing- provide maximum breathability, keeping your feet fresh throughout the day. Lace fastenings deliver a secure fit, while padded ankle collars and pull tabs to the heel offer added comfort and convenience.\nThe game-changing Max Air 270 units offer superior cushioning, shape retention, and energy absorption - making these a versatile investment buy. With 2-piece foam midsoles and rubber outsoles featuring a transparent panel, these trainers guarantee maximum comfort and durability, keeping you ready to conquer any challenge.\nWhether you\'re hitting the gym or the streets, the Nike Air Max 270 Trainers are the ultimate choice for those who appreciate high-quality gear that seamlessly blends style and performance. Gear up and unleash your full potential with these game-changing trainers!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/12105303_l_a1.jpg'),
(2510, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'The Men\'s Nike Defy All Day Mens Trainers are a great addition to any casual trainer collection, featuring a lace fastening front with a shaped ankle collar for a secure and comfortable fit with the cushioned insole and moulded outsole provide a comfortable ride, reflective detail increase your visibility and the Nike swoosh branding completes the look.', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/13107203_l_a1.jpg'),
(2511, 'Nike Air Max 270', 'Nike\'s Court Vision Mid Next Nature Shoes are a dynamic fusion of classic styles remixed and revisited- where the vibrant energy of 1980s basketballs meets the relentless spirit of 21st-century life. With their mid-top style, these shoes provide the perfect blend of support and freedom of movement.\nCrafted with recycled synthetic uppers, these mid-top kicks are fashionable and eco-friendly. The round toes and perforations to the toe boxes and sides ensure breathability and optimal airflow, keeping your feet cool and comfortable all day.\nLace them up tight, and feel the plushly padded ankle collars embrace your feet in a cushioned fit. The stylised treads on the outsoles provide unmatched traction and grip on any surface, giving you the confidence to power through your day.\nWith iconic Nike Swooshes on the sides and Nike logos on the heels, this pair symbolise style and quality. Finished with discreet tone-on-tone topstitching, these Nike Court Vision Mid Next Nature Shoes embody athletic prowess and fashion-forward design. So why wait? Gear up and take your day to the next level with these powerhouse sneakers!', 'https://www.sportsdirect.com/images/products/16105003_l_a1.jpg');
